,\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"Deliverables:\",\"avatar\":[\"57\"],\"personsName\":\"Sixteen animated and live-action functional films Airbnb Trips Reveal film and Future of Homes film Four 15-second digital ads New Airbnb Motion logo\",\"jobTitle\":\"\"}},\"178\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/231786676\",\"caption\":\"Airbnb motion logo\"}},\"155\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Let\\u2019s get functional<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We started by developing eight animated and live-action product marketing videos to introduce users to key features built into the new Airbnb app. Each video needed to be playable in both landscape and portrait mode. Double the work&hellip; double the fun.<\\/p>\"}},\"156\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"150\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"157\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"158\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177317\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Experiences\"}},\"159\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177901\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Itinerary\"}},\"160\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177150\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Co-hosting\"}},\"161\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177011\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Social Impact Experiences\"}}}}},\"162\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Our <\\/strong><strong><em>Argo<\\/em><\\/strong><strong> moment<\\/strong><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Meanwhile, Bokeh\\u2019s CEO, David, went undercover with an exuberant crew of filmmakers to old Havana, Cuba. With no time to obtain permits, we developed alibis to explain the excessive amount of camera gear. We got the greenlight thanks to some quick thinking and charming Spanglish. <\\/p>\"}},\"163\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193176889\",\"caption\":\"Staying Connected in Cuba\"}},\"164\":{\"type\":\"threeUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"152\"],\"secondImage\":[\"21\"],\"thirdImage\":[\"72\"]}},\"165\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>In the clutch<\\/strong><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Two days before the Airbnb Open, Brian needed a Hail Mary. He asked Bokeh to develop two more product videos for his keynote presentation, including the anthem piece that would be used to officially announce the launch of Airbnb Trips.<\\/p>\"}},\"166\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193184792\",\"caption\":\"Airbnb Collections Teaser | Aired During AO 2016 Keynote\"}},\"167\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"168\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/194444259\",\"caption\":\"Burlesque\"}},\"169\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193185940\",\"caption\":\"Samurai\"}},\"170\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193185835\",\"caption\":\"Runner\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193186104\",\"caption\":\"Scenester\"}}}}},\"179\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>The payoff<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The assets were leveraged across a variety of channels from Airbnb Open to product landing pages, social and YouTube, email newsletters, and paid media. The functional videos amassed over <strong>11 million views in less than three weeks<\\/strong>. On Airbnb product pages, the <strong>video click-through-rate reached as high as 15 percent<\\/strong>. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We received coverage in the <strong><em>NYTimes<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, Adweek, <\\/strong><strong><em>Travel + Leisure<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, TechCrunch, Mashable, <\\/str