 ('137', '4', '2', '1', 'en_us', '33', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Airbnb\",\"slug\":\"airbnb\",\"postDate\":1502508000,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#f62961\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>The campaign that <em>\\u201c<\\/em><em>brought the house down<\\/em><em>\\u201d<\\/em>&nbsp;at <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/bokeh\\/public_html\\/projects\\/airbnb#entry:4:url\\\">Airbnb<\\/a>.<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"222\"],\"5\":\"On November 17, 2016, Airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history. Just five weeks earlier, Bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line.\",\"10\":{\"146\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cThis film brought the house down. I cannot imagine now having done this without it.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":\"\",\"personsName\":\"Brian Chesky\",\"jobTitle\":\"CEO of Airbnb\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Mission:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>On November 17, 2016, Airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history. Just five weeks earlier, Bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Working alongside engineering, brand, product marketing, art, and C-level teams, we developed a dizzying amount of content to educate users on new features, advertise and build awareness on social media, and, ultimately, to introduce the world to Airbnb Trips on-stage at Airbnb Open in Los Angeles.<\\/p>\"}},\"153\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193175968\",\"caption\":\"Welcome to the World of Trips | Aired During Airbnb Open 2016 Keynote\"}},\"251\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding Animation<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><li>Animation<\\/li><li>Digital Ads<\\/li><li>Social Ads<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<h2>Deliverables<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>16 animated and live-action functional films<\\/li><li>Airbnb Trips Reveal and Future of Homes film<\\/li><li>4 15-second digital ads<\\/li><li>New Airbnb animated logo<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"178\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/231786676\",\"caption\":\"Airbnb motion logo\"}},\"155\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Let\\u2019s get functional<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We started by developing eight animated and live-action product marketing videos to introduce users to key features built into the new Airbnb app. Each video needed to be playable in both landscape and portrait mode. Double the work&hellip; double the fun.<\\/p>\"}},\"157\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"158\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177317\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Experiences\"}},\"159\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177901\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Itinerary\"}},\"160\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177150\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Co-hosting\"}},\"161\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177011\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Social Impact Experiences\"}}}}},\"162\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Our <\\/strong><strong><em>Argo<\\/em><\\/strong><strong> moment<\\/strong><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Meanwhile, Bokeh\\u2019s CEO, David, went undercover with an exuberant crew of filmmakers to old Havana, Cuba. With no time to obtain permits, we developed alibis to explain the excessive amount of camera gear. We got the greenlight thanks to some quick thinking and charming Spanglish. <\\/p>\"}},\"163\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193176889\",\"caption\":\"Staying Connected in Cuba\"}},\"252\":{\"type\":\"twoUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"29\"],\"secondImage\":[\"203\"]}},\"164\":{\"type\":\"threeUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"152\"],\"secondImage\":[\"21\"],\"thirdImage\":[\"72\"]}},\"165\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>In the clutch<\\/strong><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Two days before the Airbnb Open, Brian needed a Hail Mary. He asked Bokeh to develop two more product videos for his keynote presentation, including the anthem piece that would be used to officially announce the launch of Airbnb Trips.<\\/p>\"}},\"166\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193184792\",\"caption\":\"Airbnb Collections Teaser | Aired During AO 2016 Keynote\"}},\"167\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"168\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/194444259\",\"caption\":\"Burlesque\"}},\"169\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193185940\",\"caption\":\"Samurai\"}},\"170\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193185835\",\"caption\":\"Runner\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193186104\",\"caption\":\"Scenester\"}}}}},\"221\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cThis film brought the house down. I cannot imagine now having done this without it.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":\"\",\"personsName\":\"\",\"jobTitle\":\"\",\"shapeBackground\":\"\"}},\"180\":{\"type\":\"fiveUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"199\"],\"secondImage\":[\"203\"],\"thirdImage\":[\"29\"],\"fourthImage\":[\"76\"],\"fifthImage\":[\"210\"]}},\"181\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"177\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"179\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>The payoff<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The assets were leveraged across a variety of channels from Airbnb Open to product landing pages, social and YouTube, email newsletters, and paid media. The functional videos amassed over <strong>11 million views in less than three weeks<\\/strong>. On Airbnb product pages, the <strong>video click-through-rate reached as high as 15 percent<\\/strong>. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We received coverage in the <strong><em>NYTimes<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, Adweek, <\\/strong><strong><em>Travel + Leisure<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, TechCrunch, Mashable, <\\/strong><strong><em>The Telegraph<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, and Fast Company.<\\/strong><\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"96\"],\"9\":\"center\"}}', '2017-09-17 19:24:42', '2017-09-17 19:24:42', '321f7daa-62d1-43b0-b600-42b68bd69d4e'),
