 ('223', '77', '2', '75', 'en_us', '41', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Instagram\",\"slug\":\"instagram\",\"postDate\":1503364800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#4463e4\",\"63\":[\"366\"],\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>We backpacked around the globe to shoot a series for<\\/strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\">Instagram<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"210\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"282\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>The Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram\\u2019s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.<\\/p>\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"458\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"459\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181711\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the UAE\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181279\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the United Kingdom\"}},\"461\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182109\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Germany\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193179905\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Spain\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975453\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Mexico\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975723\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Italy\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975916\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Brazil\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182537\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in France\"}}}}},\"323\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Nobody\\u2019s inspired by jargon<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, &nbsp;and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.<\\/p>\"}},\"467\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/153582145\",\"caption\":\"\\\"Made on Instagram\\\" Pitch Film\"}},\"324\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Non-stop<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.<\\/p>\"}},\"492\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"29\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"493\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"432\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"494\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"470\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"490\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"488\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"325\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Breaking the Rules<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to \\u201caccidently\\u201d skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.<\\/p>\"}},\"326\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"bottom\"}}', '2017-10-05 19:01:08', '2017-10-05 19:01:08', '90659829-44a3-4c3d-9c2a-7f0d5d924b72'),
