 ('225', '367', '2', '75', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb & Resy\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-resy\",\"postDate\":1507072860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#996633\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We created a video to announce the launch of Resy on Airbnb\\u2019s app, but still had to make our own reservations.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"505\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"368\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>As part of its goal to make Airbnb a more functional app for users while they are on their trip, Airbnb partnered with Resy, a restaurant-reservation service that offers users a curated list of options&mdash;avoiding the inconvenience of having to find good food on a trip. Airbnb asked Bokeh to develop a video to announce the launch of its collaboration with Resy to offer instant restaurant reservations through the Airbnb app.<\\/p>\"}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>You Know Me, The OG<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Taking advantage of the open ended creative, we wanted to explore integrating the photorealistic UI of the product into the illustrated animation. To integrate the video with the design even further, we based our color palette around green and yellow, the colors used in the app. For the animated portion, we brought in Swedish illustrator Jonas Mosesson, who basically invented the graphic aesthetic we wanted to deploy. Rather than hire someone to imitate someone else, we\\u2019ve found that the best, most efficient way to capture a distinct style is to bring in the person who created it. The resulting illustrations he did trended on Dribble\\u2019s home page for several days.<\\/p>\"}},\"370\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Where\\u2019s Bokeh?<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Although the video was simple, we were able to include a few Easter eggs into the design, such as including our producer\\u2019s name as one of the restaurants offered.<\\/p>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/234724566\",\"caption\":\"\"}},\"371\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"511\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"509\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"508\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"507\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new5\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"506\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-05 19:26:02', '2017-10-05 19:26:02', '5218b226-799a-47a8-8957-cf7f66ad068e'),
