rs entertain themselves for five minutes and Airbnb is given five minutes of their attention. We decided to pitch a crossword puzzle.<\\/p>\"}},\"629\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"627\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"340\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The final ad ran on over 200,000 boarding passes for all Easyjet flights to Barcelona from continental Europe during March 2017. <\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"313\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-06 18:15:38', '2017-10-06 18:15:38', '4ba46a57-6e6e-4f3e-bd22-2d89584b370d'),
 ('263', '279', '2', '75', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"The Irvine Company\",\"slug\":\"the-irvine-company\",\"postDate\":1506388860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#fbcb01\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We made a video about real estate development exciting (Really.)<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"564\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"316\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission:<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>In 2016, residential real estate development and master planning company the Irvine Company asked Bokeh to create a series of videos to generate community excitement and encourage the Cupertino City Council to approve its latest development, The Hamptons, located adjacent to Apple Park.<\\/p>\"}},\"571\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/171478246\",\"caption\":\"The Hamptons, Cupertino\"}},\"318\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Focus on What Really Matters<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Architects and developers aggrandizing another luxury development wasn\\u2019t going to resonate with anyone. In our interviews, we shifted the storytelling focus away from the specific design achievements of landscape architect Laurie Olin and architect Bernardo Fort-Brescia of Arquitectonica to how the development enriched the lives of its residents and the community of Cupertino as a whole. In other words, we felt the most effective approach would be to ground our story in humanity. <\\/p>\"}},\"572\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"573\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"565\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"574\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"567\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"575\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"568\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"576\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"564\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"630\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"319\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>See the Unseen<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To make a video for a development that didn\\u2019t exist yet, we partnered with the amazing creatives at Steelblue LLC to create 3D animated renderings of the complex with real and computer generated people in each space.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>First, they built out the CGI spaces with camera moves so we could make them consistent with the live-action shots. To make these homes feel active and alive, we asked Steelblue to fill up a green screen studio with a ton of extras. In fact, it was the most extras Steelblue had ever included in a single scene. It was also the first time they shot live extras swimming in a CGI pool. Using this combination of animation, interviews, aerial imagery, and B-roll footage, Bokeh made a real estate video with life and heart.<\\/p>\"}},\"320\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The cut-downs<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>It\\u2019s not easy to cover every detail of a multi-million dollar development in a single video. So we created a short series of topical cutdowns that highlighted The Hamptons\\u2019 most impressive features.<\\/p>\"}},\"578\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"579\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412289\",\"caption\":\"Sustainability\"}},\"580\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412287\",\"caption\":\"Planning Principles\"}},\"581\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412286\",\"caption\":\"Public Promenade\"}},\"582\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412285\",\"caption\":\"Building Composition\"}},\"583\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412284\",\"caption\":\"Perimeter Trail\"}},\"584\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412279\",\"caption\":\"Landscape\"}}}}},\"321\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Hallelujah Housing<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The Hamptons passed the city council and the master plan was approved. Hallelujah! We have housing.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"315\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-06 18:40:51', '2017-10-06 18:40:51', '877969fe-e1e3-47eb-861e-9cc16cfa6070'),
 ('264', '330', '2', '75', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Play\",\"slug\":\"google-play\",\"postDate\":1507055400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#43cd26\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Our parents thought this Google Play April Fool\'s joke was real. Success!<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"653\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"331\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The team at Google Play was certain about two things. First, they wanted a video to commemorate the April Fool\\u2019s holiday. Second, they wanted the video to involve pets. With these parameters outlined, Bokeh went to work to develop a hilarious and entertaining video to introduce <em>Google Play for Pets<\\/em>.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"332\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/video<\\/li><li>Animation<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/213573065\",\"caption\":\"Google Play for Pets\"}},\"333\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Make it believable<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We made the conscious decision to avoid cheap laughs and cute gimmicks; to create an April Fool\\u2019s video that took itself and its intent to lead the audience astray seriously. The story&mdash;and the product at its center&mdash;had to be grounded in a real-world logic that the viewer could \\u201calmost\\u201d follow. We needed to develop a product idea that was simple, and solved a real human issue.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our proposal: Google Play is introducing a new category of apps in the Play Store to help pet owners train their pets and keep them occupied while they\\u2019re away.<\\/p>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"641\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\