tivity and heart.\"}}},\"64\":{\"292\":{\"type\":\"textWithVideo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"How do we say our name? Is it:\",\"video\":[\"290\"]}},\"293\":{\"type\":\"textWithVideo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"Funnily enough, we don\'t know.\",\"video\":[\"286\"]}},\"294\":{\"type\":\"multiTextWithVideo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":{\"299\":{\"type\":\"4\",\"fields\":{\"line1\":\"David and doug went to film school.\",\"line2\":\"Sebastian went to business school.\",\"line3\":\"We all graduated with one goal: to create something awesome.\"}}},\"video\":[\"285\"]}},\"295\":{\"type\":\"textWithVideo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"So we started a business and made a pledge to never stop creating.\",\"video\":[\"287\"]}},\"296\":{\"type\":\"textWithVideo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"Little did we know where that would lead.\",\"video\":[\"289\"]}},\"297\":{\"type\":\"textWithVideo\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"The promise we made ourselves and our team is the promise we make you.\",\"video\":[\"291\"]}},\"298\":{\"type\":\"textWithVideoAndCta\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"Inspiration isn\'t static. It moves.\",\"video\":[\"288\"],\"cta\":{\"300\":{\"type\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"Let\'s Ride\",\"ctaLink\":\"mailto:hello@seebokeh.com\"}}}}}},\"57\":{\"275\":{\"type\":\"word\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"word\":\"creative\"}},\"276\":{\"type\":\"word\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"word\":\"strategy\"}},\"277\":{\"type\":\"word\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"word\":\"design\"}},\"278\":{\"type\":\"word\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"word\":\"digital\"}}},\"62\":\"236600268\"}}', '2017-10-06 23:19:32', '2017-10-06 23:19:32', 'a4cc44a0-0e27-47cf-8460-0d77f824a602'),
 ('288', '360', '2', '75', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb NYC Experiences\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-nyc-experiences\",\"postDate\":1507072500,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#ff4848\",\"63\":[\"302\"],\"4\":\"<p>Approved Friday, organized Saturday, took off Sunday. That was&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-nyc-experiences#entry:360:url\\\">Airbnb Experiences<\\/a>&nbsp;NYC.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"372\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"361\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb Experiences offers classes, tours, and other activities with locals to connect visitors with their surroundings in a fresh, meaningful way. Already live in a handful of cities, Airbnb asked Bokeh to produce the multichannel launch of Airbnb Experiences in New York. Bokeh had to wing it (literally) to the Big Apple to capture unique experiences in all five boroughs in just four days.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To create the assets&mdash;videos, content copy, b2b, PR and social images&mdash;Bokeh took our coordination skills to new heights, not only working among Airbnb\\u2019s own art, PR, social, and marketing teams, but with photographers, videographers, and models to ensure seamless timing and transitioning.<\\/p>\"}},\"362\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><li>Photography<\\/li><li>Social<\\/li><li>Product<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"409\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/235420494\",\"caption\":\"\"}},\"363\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>All Together Now<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>On the front end, we had to get all of the departments involved in the same room to identify individual needs and help convey the larger picture to everyone involved. After reviewing their wish lists, we consolidated them to create deliverables as smoothly and simultaneously as possible.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Then, we choreographed the production itself, prioritizing the anthem video but making sure that each photographer, videographer, and even \\u201ciPhoneagrapher\\u201d could get the shots needed fluidly and efficiently.<\\/p>\"}},\"421\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"418\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"364\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Empire State of Mind<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>For Airbnb Experiences New York, we wanted to ooze NYC vibes. We relied on bold cues, such as music and iconic New York scenes, but also incorporated a quick-cut editing style and, dynamic moving shots. To really hit that frenetic city pace, we centered the transitions on travel, including taxis, subways, and busy streets.<\\/p>\"}},\"411\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"412\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"378\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Harvest Honey with Asher\\\" Experience\"}},\"420\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"376\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Harvest Honey with Asher\\\" Experience\"}},\"413\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"381\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Be Greek with Angelis\\\" Experience\"}},\"423\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"383\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Be Greek with Angelis\\\" Experience\"}},\"422\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"395\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Design Jewelry with Dynasty and Soull\\\" Experience\"}},\"414\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"398\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Design Jewelry with Dynasty and Soull\\\" Experience\"}},\"415\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"402\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Design Jewelry with Dynasty and Soull\\\" Experience\"}},\"416\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"391\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"M