com\\/168412279\",\"caption\":\"Landscape\"}}}}},\"321\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Hallelujah Housing<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The Hamptons passed the city council and the master plan was approved. Hallelujah! We have housing.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"315\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-07 03:55:39', '2017-10-07 03:55:39', 'ea99246e-9d67-4140-a72d-45873ff02d28'),
 ('310', '77', '2', '75', 'en_us', '47', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Instagram for Business\",\"slug\":\"instagram\",\"postDate\":1503364800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#4463e4\",\"63\":[\"366\"],\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>We backpacked around the globe to shoot a series for<\\/strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\">Instagram<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"235\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"282\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>The Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram\\u2019s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.<\\/p>\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"458\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"459\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181711\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the UAE\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181279\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the United Kingdom\"}},\"461\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182109\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Germany\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193179905\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Spain\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975453\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Mexico\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975723\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Italy\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975916\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Brazil\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182537\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in France\"}}}}},\"323\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Nobody\\u2019s inspired by jargon<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, &nbsp;and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.<\\/p>\"}},\"467\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/153582145\",\"caption\":\"\\\"Made on Instagram\\\" Pitch Film\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"324\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Non-stop<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.<\\/p>\"}},\"492\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"498\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"29\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"493\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"432\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"494\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"470\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"490\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"488\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"325\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Breaking the Rules<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to \\u201caccidently\\u201d skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.<\\/p>\"}},\"499\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"497\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"326\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"bottom\"}}', '2017-10-07 03:56:16', '2017-10-07 03:56:16', '4e2f7af8-74e4-4ec0-9138-a544dfdc62bf'),
 ('311', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1507331340,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#000000\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We helped kick of World Environment Day at Expo Milano 2015!<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"690\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-07 03:56:30', '2017-10-07 03:56:30', 'f89fbfeb-70e0-49fc-869a-f829b881f265'),
 ('312', '367', '2', '75', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb & Resy\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-resy\",\"postDate\":1507072860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0d6774\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We created a video to announce the launch of Resy on Airbnb\\u2019s app, but still had to make our own reservations.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"509\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"368\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>As part of its goal to make Airbnb a more functional app for users while they are on their trip, Airbnb partnered with Resy, a restaurant-reservation service that offers users a curated list of options&mdash;avoiding the inconvenience of having to find good food on a trip. Airbnb asked Bokeh to develop a video to announce the launch of its collaboration with Resy to offer instant restaurant reservations through the Airbnb app.<\\/p>\"}},\"524\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"522\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"515\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"516\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"511\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"525\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"510\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"517\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"509\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"518\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"508\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"507\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"520\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"506\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>You Know Me, The OG<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Taking advantage of the open ended creative, we wanted to explore integrating the photorealistic UI of the product into the illustrated animation. To integrate the video with the design even further, we based our color palette around green and yellow, the colors used in the app. For the animated portion, we brought in Swedish illustrator Jonas Mosesson, who basically invented the graphic aesthetic we wanted to deploy. Rather than hire someone to imitate someone else, we\\u2019ve found that the best, most efficient way to capture a distinct style is to bring in the person who created it. The resulting illustrations he did trended on Dribble\\u2019s home page for several days.<\\/p>\"}},\"370\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Where\\u2019s Bokeh?<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Although the video was simple, we were able to include a few Easter eggs into the design, such as including our producer\\u2019s name as one of the restaurants offered.<\\/p>\"}},\"514\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/234724566\",\"caption\":\"\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"371\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\"}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-07 03:58:01', '2017-10-07 03:58:01', 'd489f1b0-b1fd-4e97-8d31-eab78771e9d2'),
