\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Sharp shooter<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Photography is a tricky business. Hefty day-rates, agency fees, licensing and license renewals inflate costs and add time. They place extra burden to our partners, and keep us from working lean. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To make our photoshoots faster, more flexible, and better suited to the digital age we developed new relationships with independent freelancers who understood the evolving media environment We also were able to maximize content output by pairing photography with active video productions and vice versa.<\\/p>\"}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"802\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"781\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"803\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"784\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"783\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"786\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"782\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"771\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\"}}},\"2\":[\"766\",\"359\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-09 01:05:49', '2017-10-09 01:05:49', '89830d1a-75cf-4fa7-a70f-6c700adfd25a'),
 ('431', '762', '2', '75', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb Vacation Rentals\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-vacation-rentals\",\"postDate\":1507497960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#ffb500\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We told a story the vacation rentals community could own for <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-vacation-rentals#entry:762\\\">Airbnb<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"549\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"763\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb cofounder and CSO Nathan Blecharczyk was a keynote speaker at the Vacation Rental Managers Association national conference in Orlando, Florida. Airbnb tasked Bokeh with creating a video that conveyed Airbnb\\u2019s brand values of human connection and empathy.<\\/p>\"}},\"764\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Not just passing through<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb has been somewhat of a dark horse in the vacation rental community and Nathan\\u2019s presentation needed to recognize that issue and connect to potential new hosts. As part of that ambition, we opted for a documentary-style film that told the story of a host and his business without relying on Airbnb talking points. We found Steve Frellick of Yonder Luxury Home Rentals in Asheville, North Carolina. Steve was on the brink of foreclosure during the recession of 2008 when his bank suggested he take one year to turn the family home he built himself into a vacation rental. He was so successful renting it on Airbnb that he now owns 80 properties. His story not only encapsulates an inherently American narrative, but his humility, passion, and empathy for his guests carries authentic emotional weight.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>From a strategic standpoint, featuring a business built in North Carolina would be culturally relevant to the audience. There are a lot of vacation rentals in the Southeast and, as the conference was in Orlando, many people attending would find personal connections to a local story.<\\/p>\"}},\"765\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>1+1=1,000,000<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><\\/p><p>We felt Steve\\u2019s story had a heart to resonate with other vacation rental owners. Our film was a character study and a community study that aligned their interests with Airbnb\\u2019s ethos of seeking common interests and forging connections.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Throughout the narrative, Steve explains how much his business means to him and his family above and beyond financial necessity. He walks through Pine Hollow, the house he and his wife built for their family, and points out a wood beam where he used to mark his children\\u2019s heights&mdash;guests now add their heights to the same post. When people were evacuating from the hurricanes, Steve shares how he was able to help them, and, in turn, how Airbnb helped him accomplish that. These details are imperative and speak to a community focus, loving attention to detail, and a meaningful guest-host relationship; qualities that have been key Airbnb\\u2019s success.<span><\\/span><br><\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"359\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-09 18:57:35', '2017-10-09 18:57:35', 'aded1318-d60a-4439-850c-0062d374caf9'),
 ('432', '767', '2', '75', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Local Guides\",\"slug\":\"google-local-guides\",\"postDate\":1507499580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#e46a4a\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We did a Photo-Worthy Photoshoot for Google <\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"779\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"768\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Google Local Guides is a program where users leave reviews and upload photos of their favorite places so that others can find and experience them too. In September 2015, we were asked to conceptualize and produce bright and colorful photography that spoke to the values at the heart of the Local Guides brand&mdash;discovery, sharing, community.<\\/p>\"}},\"808\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"777\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"769\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Location, location, location<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We started by identifying the cool local places that would resonate most with millennials (i.e. us.). We wanted to show spots slightly off the beaten path that people would be genuinely excited to share. The final list included places such as Pizzeria Delfina, Shark Fin Cove, Philz, the Santa Cruz Beach Boardwalk, and Chantal Guillon Macarons.<\\/p>\"}},\"809\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"807\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"795\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"796\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"787\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"797\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"780\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"798\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"788\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"799\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"778\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"800\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"776\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"770\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Sharp shooter<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Photography is a tricky business. Hefty day-rates, agency fees, licensing and license renewals inflate costs and add time. They place extra burden to our partners, and keep us from working lean. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To make our photoshoots faster, more flexible, and better suited to the digital age we developed new relationships with independent freelancers who understood the evolving media environment We also were able to maximize content output by pairing photography with active video productions and vice versa.<\\/p>\"}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"802\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"811\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"803\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"815\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"813\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"812\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"810\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"771\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\"}}},\"2\":[\"766\",\"359\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-09 19:03:40', '2017-10-09 19:03:40', 'a8326e15-7704-48c5-a533-24a5b28cd385'),
