\":{\"743\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"730\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"745\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"728\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"744\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"740\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"755\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"752\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"756\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"753\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"757\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"754\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"761\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Text goes here<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-12 23:01:31', '2017-10-12 23:01:31', '504ba39a-0317-4580-ab18-c5d15df42a39'),
 ('451', '767', '2', '75', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Local Guides\",\"slug\":\"google-local-guides\",\"postDate\":1507499580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#f4ac1b\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We did a Photo-Worthy Photoshoot for Google <\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"779\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"768\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Google Local Guides is a program where users leave reviews and upload photos of their favorite places so that others can find and experience them too. In September 2015, we were asked to conceptualize and produce bright and colorful photography that spoke to the values at the heart of the Local Guides brand&mdash;discovery, sharing, community. The final images would be incorporated into the Google Local Guides microsite.<\\/p>\"}},\"809\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"807\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"769\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Location, location, location<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We started by identifying the cool local places that would resonate most with millennials (i.e. us.). We wanted to show spots slightly off the beaten path that people would be genuinely excited to share. The final list included places such as Pizzeria Delfina, Shark Fin Cove, Philz, the Santa Cruz Beach Boardwalk, and Chantal Guillon Macarons.<\\/p>\"}},\"770\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Sharp shooter<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Photography is a tricky business. Hefty day-rates, agency fees, licensing and license renewals inflate costs and add time. They place extra burden to our partners, and keep us from working lean. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To make our photoshoots faster, more flexible, and better suited to the digital age we developed new relationships with independent freelancers who understood the evolving media environment We also were able to maximize content output by pairing photography with active video productions and vice versa.<\\/p>\"}},\"771\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><\\/p>\"}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"803\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"815\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"802\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"811\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"813\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"812\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"810\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}}},\"2\":[\"766\",\"359\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-12 23:10:23', '2017-10-12 23:10:23', '3042239b-13d8-43c7-a0c0-d5d5f69cd6cb'),
 ('452', '360', '2', '75', 'en_us', '41', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb NYC Experiences\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-nyc-experiences\",\"postDate\":1507072500,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#f24733\",\"63\":[\"817\"],\"4\":\"<p>We visited 5 boroughs in 4 days to help launch <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-nyc-experiences#entry:360:url\\\">Airbnb Experiences<\\/a> in New York<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"372\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"361\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Since launching Trips in November 2016, Airbnb Experiences has connected travellers with classes, tours, and activities hosted by locals in a handful of cities around the world with one blaring exception: <strong>New York City<\\/strong>. A little under two weeks before launch, Airbnb asked Bokeh to conceptualize and execute a true multichannel production. We captured five unique experiences in each of the five boroughs in just four days of production to create assets leveraged across marketing, PR, social, and in-product.<\\/p>\"}},\"362\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><li>Photography<\\/li><li>Social<\\/li><li>Product<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"409\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/235420494\",\"caption\":\"\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"363\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>All Together Now<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>On the front end, we wrangled together Airbnb\\u2019s product marketing, PR, social and art departments in the same room to help identify individual objectives, and shape the larger picture for our production. After reviewing each team\\u2019s wish list of content, we consolidated them to create an production approach that would fulfill everyone\\u2019s needs.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p> <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The production was shaped around our anthem video for product marketing. Leveraging this infrastructure, we choreographed a Camera B team to collect in-product trailers for the Airbnb app, the photographer to collect PR content, and am iPhonographer to capture vertical assets for Instagram and Instagram stories.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"421\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"418\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"364\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Empire State of Mind<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We wanted to embody the attitude and swagger of New York City. For the videos that meant paying homage to New York\\u2019s jazz and hip hop culture with the soundtrack, as well as employing a quick-cut editing style and dynamic movements. These gritty exterior shots were layered with displays of genuine human connection and discovery on the part of our guests&mdash;regular people (not models) who joined us on each Experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The end goal was to show that the hosts were products of New York and the experiences were products of the hosts; these adventures could not happen anywhere else. This intent permeated through all of our work: photography included portraits of each host in their respective locations surrounded by the elements of their experiences, from bespoke hats to Greek tapas, and social media assets were shaped as \\u201ctakeovers\\u201d so the hosts could communicate to Airbnb\\u2019s audiences in a way that was both casual and captivating. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The deliverables were colorful, real and packed with sincere exploration and camaraderie.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p> <\\/p>\"}},\"411\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"412\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"378\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Harvest Honey with Asher\\\" Experience\"}},\"420\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"376\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Harvest Honey with Asher\\\" Experience\"}},\"413\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"381\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Be Greek with Angelis\\\" Experience\"}},\"423\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"383\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Be Greek with Angelis\\\" Experience\"}},\"422\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"395\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Design Jewelry with Dynasty and Soull\\\" Experience\"}},\"414\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"398\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Design Jewelry with Dynasty and Soull\\\" Experience\"}},\"415\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"402\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Design Jewelry with Dynasty and Soull\\\" Experience\"}},\"416\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"391\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Make a Hat with Brandon\\\" Experience\"}},\"427\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"394\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Make a Hat with Brandon\\\" Experience\"}},\"429\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"388\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Street Dance with It\'s Showtime NYC!\\\" Experience\"}},\"424\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"407\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Sail NYC History with Matt\\\" Experience\"}},\"430\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"404\"],\"caption\":\"Still from the \\\"Sail NYC History with Matt\\\" Experience\"}}}}},\"365\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\"}},\"694\":{\"type\":\"threeSideBySideImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"827\"],\"secondImage\":[\"816\"],\"thirdImage\":[\"826\"]}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"358\",\"359\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-15 18:17:05', '2017-10-15 18:17:05', '0fbc2e49-e179-4ffb-b349-90d789d268fa'),
