es an inherently American narrative, but his humility, passion, and empathy for his guests carries authentic emotional weight.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>From a strategic standpoint, featuring a business built in North Carolina would be culturally relevant to the audience. There are a lot of vacation rentals in the Southeast and, as the conference was in Orlando, many people attending would find personal connections to a local story.<\\/p>\"}},\"765\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>1+1=1,000,000<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We felt Steve\\u2019s story had a heart to resonate with other vacation rental owners. Our film was a character study and a community study that aligned their interests with Airbnb\\u2019s ethos of seeking common interests and forging connections.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Throughout the narrative, Steve explains how much his business means to him and his family above and beyond financial necessity. He walks through Pine Hollow, the house he and his wife built for their family, and points out a wood beam where he used to mark his children\\u2019s heights&mdash;guests now add their heights to the same post. When people were evacuating from the hurricanes, Steve shares how he was able to help them, and, in turn, how Airbnb helped him accomplish that. These details are imperative and speak to a community focus, loving attention to detail, and a meaningful guest-host relationship; qualities that have been key Airbnb\\u2019s success.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"920\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"921\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"918\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"922\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"917\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"923\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"908\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"924\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"907\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"925\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"909\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"926\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"915\"],\"caption\"