 ('510', '367', '2', '75', 'en_us', '45', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb & Resy\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-resy\",\"postDate\":1507072860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-resy#entry:367:url\\\">Airbnb partnered with Resy<\\/a> to launch restaurant reservations. We still couldn\'t get a table.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"509\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"368\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To make Airbnb a more functional app for travelers during a trip, Airbnb partnered with Resy to offer a curated list of restaurants&mdash;from local favorites to award winners&mdash;and make it easy to book a table right in the app. Bokeh was asked to develop an illustration style to create a&nbsp; fun animated video and email campaign to announce the launch of this new feature in 16 major markets across the U.S.<\\/p>\"}},\"524\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"695\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Swede and simple<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We wanted to explore integrating the photorealistic UI of the product into the illustrated animation. This combination allowed us to actually show Resy in action on the Airbnb app, creating a video that was informative and clear, but also colorful and entertaining.<\\/p>\"}},\"858\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"857\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"845\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>For the animated portions, we based our color palette around green and yellow, the colors used in the app rather than Airbnb\\u2019s signature Rausch. By utilizing Kazan and Beach, we offered a fresh take on Airbnb\\u2019s palette while still keeping it tied to the brand.<\\/p>\"}},\"847\":{\"type\":\"inlineI