 ('521', '672', '2', '75', 'en_us', '17', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Wealthfront\",\"slug\":\"wealthfront\",\"postDate\":1507331400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Animating your journey to financial stability<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"725\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1><p>Financial management company Wealthfront offers software and apps to help people oversee their money in a straightforward way using robotic algorithms. Bokeh was brought on to make an informational animated video for the launch of Wealthfront\\u2019s new product, Path, a visual app that makes it easy for people to plan, track, and save for retirement. <\\/p>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1><ul><li>Animated product launch video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"722\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/202971604\",\"caption\":\"Path by Wealthfront\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"717\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"712\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Wheel it out<\\/h1><p>Wealthfront already had an illustration style and color palette in place on its site and wanted the video to fit that framework. Additionally, they asked us to convey a sense of active lifestyle. With these parameters, as well as the ultimate goal to convey the product information in an engaging way, we opted for a narrative centered on a woman biking&mdash;a metaphor for the ups and downs in life. We finessed the design to make sure it felt native to the existing site and used visual cues, such as increasingly expensive cars and larger homes, to illustrate the technical talking points in a lighthearted manner. <\\/p>\"}},\"720\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"723\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1><p>This video was used in e-mail blast to Wealthfront\\u2019s vast audience of users to inform them about Path. This animation was also used on the main landing page for the dedicated Path website.<\\/p>\"}},\"721\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"714\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:23:40', '2017-10-23 18:23:40', 'a5544aad-f2e1-44ec-be13-6bcfeebe5d44'),
 ('522', '672', '2', '75', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Wealthfront\",\"slug\":\"wealthfront\",\"postDate\":1507331400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Animating your journey to financial stability<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"725\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"958\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Financial management company Wealthfront offers software and apps to help people oversee their money in a straightforward way using robotic algorithms. Bokeh was brought on to make an informational animated video for the launch of Wealthfront\\u2019s new product, Path, a visual app that makes it easy for people to plan, track, and save for retirement. <\\/p>\"}},\"959\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Animated product launch video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"722\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/202971604\",\"caption\":\"Path by Wealthfront\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"717\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"712\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"960\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Wheel it out<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Wealthfront already had an illustration style and color palette in place on its site and wanted the video to fit that framework. Additionally, they asked us to convey a sense of active lifestyle. With these parameters, as well as the ultimate goal to convey the product information in an engaging way, we opted for a narrative centered on a woman biking&mdash;a metaphor for the ups and downs in life. We finessed the design to make sure it felt native to the existing site and used visual cues, such as increasingly expensive cars and larger homes, to illustrate the technical talking points in a lighthearted manner. <\\/p>\"}},\"720\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"723\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"961\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>This video was used in e-mail blast to Wealthfront\\u2019s vast audience of users to inform them about Path. This animation was also used on the main landing page for the dedicated Path website.<\\/p>\"}},\"721\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"714\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:23:48', '2017-10-23 18:23:48', 'fc312c89-b346-49fc-ba30-93d031c4be4b'),
 ('523', '367', '2', '75', 'en_us', '47', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb & Resy\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-resy\",\"postDate\":1507072860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-resy#entry:367:url\\\">Airbnb partnered with Resy<\\/a> to launch restaurant reservations. We still couldn\'t get a table.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"509\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"368\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To make Airbnb a more functional app for travelers during a trip, Airbnb partnered with Resy to offer a curated list of restaurants&mdash;from local favorites to award winners&mdash;and make it easy to book a table right in the app. Bokeh was asked to develop an illustration style to create a&nbsp; fun animated video and email campaign to announce the launch of this new feature in 16 major markets across the U.S.<\\/p>\"}},\"524\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"695\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Swede and simple<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We wanted to explore integrating the photorealistic UI of the product into the illustrated animation. This combination allowed us to actually show Resy in action on the Airbnb app, creating a video that was informative and clear, but also colorful and entertaining.<\\/p>\"}},\"858\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"857\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"845\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>For the animated portions, we based our color palette around green and yellow, the colors used in the app rather than Airbnb\\u2019s signature Rausch. By utilizing Kazan and Beach, we offered a fresh take on Airbnb\\u2019s palette while still keeping it tied to the brand.<\\/p>\"}},\"847\":{\"type\":\"inlineI