 ('526', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1507331340,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0092ff\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video shot around the world without leaving our office<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"690\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The video\\u2019s message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. <\\/p>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Anthem video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Stock up<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.<\\/p>\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"Our video played in New York\'s Time Square.\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New York\\u2019s Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEP\\u2019s displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:28:43', '2017-10-23 18:28:43', '0c15842f-7f07-4ac7-91dd-ea058f9ef65a'),
 ('527', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1507331340,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0092ff\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video shot around the world without leaving our office<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"690\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"964\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The video\\u2019s message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. <\\/p>\"}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Anthem video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Stock up<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.<\\/p>\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"Our video played in New York\'s Time Square.\"}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New York\\u2019s Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEP\\u2019s displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:28:57', '2017-10-23 18:28:57', '7512d3d3-a1fb-4f48-9477-b417b5220f0d'),
 ('528', '674', '2', '75', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"ON24\",\"slug\":\"on24\",\"postDate\":1507331460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#6ccaf4\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We Made a Video that Landed ON24 ON\\ud83d\\udcaf<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"642\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>ON24, a webinar marketing platform that offers branded video and presentation software to businesses, wanted a B2B product video that was informational, but unconventional. We challenged ourselves to level up with a hybrid live-action and integrated motion graphic approach to make a traditional B2B commercial fresh and fun.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><\\/p>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Gettin\' Disney with it<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To properly demonstrate the webinar software, the video needed to be set in an office. But, rather than use a typical, boring office environment, we created an abstract workplace in an all-white cyclorama studio. This set-up also lent itself well to the overall metaphor that even though the client and marketer are sitting next to each other, they can\\u2019t connect&mdash;until ON24 saves the day of course.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We layered these live-action office scene with motion graphics. The trick was to make the graphics feel as integrated with the live shots as possible to make the product shine and keep viewers engaged. This included having an animated Twitter bird tug at the character\\u2019s hair, floating icons, and a screen pop-up and rustle a pile of papers on a desk. <\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:37:56', '2017-10-23 18:37:56', 'a23f6e09-b791-42dd-89fd-9b45ace91eed'),
 ('529', '674', '2', '75', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"ON24\",\"slug\":\"on24\",\"postDate\":1507331460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#6ccaf4\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We Made a Video that Landed ON24 ON\\ud83d\\udcaf<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"642\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"968\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>ON24, a webinar marketing platform that offers branded video and presentation software to businesses, wanted a B2B product video that was informational, but unconventional. We challenged ourselves to level up with a hybrid live-action and integrated motion graphic approach to make a traditional B2B commercial fresh and fun.<\\/p>\"}},\"969\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Gettin\' Disney with it<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To properly demonstrate the webinar software, the video needed to be set in an office. But, rather than use a typical, boring office environment, we created an abstract workplace in an all-white cyclorama studio. This set-up also lent itself well to the overall metaphor that even though the client and marketer are sitting next to each other, they can\\u2019t connect&mdash;until ON24 saves the day of course.<\\/p><p>We layered these live-action office scene with motion graphics. The trick was to make the graphics feel as integrated with the live shots as possible to make the product shine and keep viewers engaged. This included having an animated Twitter bird tug at the character\\u2019s hair, floating icons, and a screen pop-up and rustle a pile of papers on a desk.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:39:06', '2017-10-23 18:39:06', '6851ac83-29d0-4448-b610-c7f310d84374'),
 ('530', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1507331340,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0092ff\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video shot around the world without leaving our office<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"970\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"964\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The video\\u2019s message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. <\\/p>\"}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Anthem video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Stock up<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.<\\/p>\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"Our video played in New York\'s Time Square.\"}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New York\\u2019s Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEP\\u2019s displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 18:45:13', '2017-10-23 18:45:13', 'b85f0fd8-1f73-47fa-b80a-c937386382dd'),
 ('531', '682', '2', '75', 'en_us', '19', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UberRUSH\",\"slug\":\"uberrush\",\"postDate\":1507331640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Uber wouldn\'t cover our Uber rides in NYC.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"726\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"760\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1><b>Mission<\\/b><\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Uber hired Bokeh to make the launch film for UberRUSH, which uses its network of drivers and bicycle couriers to pick up and deliver items from stores and retailers that don\\u2019t offer courier services. UberRUSH would launch in New York first, so we used the city as our backdrop and focused on three deliverable areas: food (Indie Fresh, a mason jar meal company), clothing ( Sam & Lex, an upscale boutique) and flowers (Ode \\u00e1 La Rose, a flower shop).<\\/p>\"}},\"759\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"727\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/138801682\",\"caption\":\"UberRush, Your On-Demand Network\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"746\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"747\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"731\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"748\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"737\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"749\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"729\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"750\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"736\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"751\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"735\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"825\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cI\\u2019ve worked with Bokeh on a number of projects. They consistently deliver beautiful content while remaining extremely agile in dealing with the evolving landscape of technology - something rare to find in an agency.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":\"\",\"personsName\":\"Dave Kim\",\"jobTitle\":\"Producer Marketing Manager, Uber\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"741\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"734\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"761\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Made in Manhattan<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>With the location (New York) and the shops (Indie Fresh, Sam & Lex, and Ode \\u00e1 La Rose) locked in, we focused on producing a video that embodied the vim and vigor of Manhattan, using a quick cut editing style and visually following the goods en route from store to consumer. However, we made the video before the UberRUSH app existed, so we had to anticipate what it might look like and employ another app that would track users\\u2019 fingers on the screen. When the product was ready, we were able to attach it to the screen so that it was crisp and perfectly aligned with the video.<\\/p>\"}},\"742\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"743\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"730\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"745\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"728\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"744\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"740\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"755\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"752\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"756\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"753\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"757\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"754\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Payoff<\\/h1>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-23 20:07:25', '2017-10-23 20:07:25', 'b4c522e7-6655-43b7-8a9b-890dd6e28ff8'),
 ('532', '28', '2', '75', 'en_us', '40', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Philz Coffee\",\"slug\":\"philz-coffee\",\"postDate\":1502594280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":[\"823\"],\"4\":\"<p>We cold called <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/philz-coffee#entry:28:url\\\">Philz Coffee<\\/a> to complain about their logo, and they let us do a rebrand.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"973\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"32\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Bokeh took the unconventional approach of exploring Philz\\u2019s brand identity, refreshing it, and sending a new brand deck directly to Philz\\u2019s CEO, Jacob Jaber. With custom coffee blends and a customer experience like no other, we felt that Philz deserved a brand it could fully own. The plan worked! Throughout the course of 2016, Bokeh worked intimately with the Philz team to define a uniform brand strategy that would serve as a guide for future growth. <\\/p>\"}},\"327\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Workshops<\\/li><li>Strategy<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Brand Book & Guidelines<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"35\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"56\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"328\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Talk it Out<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Philz need a distinct vision, mission, and set of values that could be embraced internally and expressed in every decision they made. So we conducted individual interviews, a series of leadership workshops, and a company off-site to provide safe spaces to debate ideas and tinker with concepts. <\\/p>\"}},\"329\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Trippin\\u2019 on research<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>White-space exercises and market research helped us create a profile for the typical Philz customer and to understand the perception of the Philz brand compared to that of its competitors. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our research survey in San Francisco\\u2019s Bay Area, Los Angeles, and Washington, D.C. complemented the statistical analysis with in-person observations and on-site customer interviews.<\\/p>\"}},\"33\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\\"The depth of each slide is quite impressive and on-point. I appreciate your quick-wittedness, intuition and aesthetic\\u2026 I think you know us better than we know ourselves.\\\"\",\"avatar\":[\"57\"],\"personsName\":\"Jacob Jaber\",\"jobTitle\":\"CEO\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"34\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=wxLUj1Mrars\",\"caption\":\"Caption\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"50\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The style guide<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><em>Real<\\/em>, <em>warm<\\/em>, <em>undaunted<\\/em>, <em>relaxed<\\/em>, <em>neighborly<\\/em>, <em>light-hearted<\\/em>, and <em>unpretentious<\\/em> are the attributes infused throughout the new Philz brand identity. Starting with the logo and brand mark, we developed a custom system of colors, typography, illustrations, and iconography with guidelines.<\\/p>\"}},\"36\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"57\"],\"caption\":\"Coffee Beanz\"}},\"51\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Philz chose to pace the launch of the new branding by starting with in-store menus, wayfinding signage, and promotional newsletters.<\\/p>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"972\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"313\",\"314\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"center\"}}', '2017-10-23 20:41:21', '2017-10-23 20:41:21', '4cc8b1db-797b-49de-b52b-38848a2152ad'),
