":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Payoff<\\/h1>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:20:25', '2017-10-24 17:20:25', '96db1ddc-fd21-4e92-8713-b0066191b3b2'),
 ('555', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1433545740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0092ff\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video shot around the world without leaving our office<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"970\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"964\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The video\\u2019s message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. <\\/p>\"}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Anthem video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Stock up<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.<\\/p>\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"Our video played in New York\'s Time Square.\"}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New York\\u2019s Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEP\\u2019s displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:22:00', '2017-10-24 17:22:00', '2a8e5cec-54ba-4c5c-ae61-b3850e9cea35'),
 ('556', '767', '2', '75', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Local Guides\",\"slug\":\"google-local-guides\",\"postDate\":1441144380,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#f4ac1b\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We did a Photo-Worthy Photoshoot for Google <\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"779\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"768\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Google Local Guides is a program where users leave reviews and upload photos of their favorite places so that others can find and experience them too. In September 2015, we were asked to conceptualize and produce bright and colorful photography that spoke to the values at the heart of the Local Guides brand&mdash;discovery, sharing, community. The final images would be incorporated into the Google Local Guides microsite.<\\/p>\"}},\"809\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"807\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"769\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Location, location, location<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We started by identifying the cool local places that would resonate most with millennials (i.e. us.). We wanted to show spots slightly off the beaten path that people would be genuinely excited to share. The final list included places such as Pizzeria Delfina, Shark Fin Cove, Philz, the Santa Cruz Beach Boardwalk, and Chantal Guillon Macarons.<\\/p>\"}},\"771\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\"}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"803\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"815\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"802\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"811\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"813\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"812\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"810\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}}},\"2\":[\"766\",\"359\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:22:28', '2017-10-24 17:22:28', '05d2ffc0-7826-47af-99cf-5db49529460a'),
 ('557', '682', '2', '75', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UberRUSH\",\"slug\":\"uberrush\",\"postDate\":1438470840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We helped Uber make a video to announce their newest service: UberRUSH<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"726\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"760\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1><strong>Mission<\\/strong><\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Uber hired Bokeh to make the launch film for UberRUSH, which uses its network of drivers and bicycle couriers to pick up and deliver items from stores and retailers that don\\u2019t offer courier services. UberRUSH would launch in New York first, so we used the city as our backdrop and focused on three deliverable areas: food (Indie Fresh, a mason jar meal company), clothing ( Sam & Lex, an upscale boutique) and flowers (Ode \\u00e1 La Rose, a flower shop).<\\/p>\"}},\"759\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"727\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/138801682\",\"caption\":\"UberRush, Your On-Demand Network\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"746\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"747\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"731\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"748\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"737\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"749\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"729\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"750\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"736\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"751\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"735\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"825\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cI\\u2019ve worked with Bokeh on a number of projects. They consistently deliver beautiful content while remaining extremely agile in dealing with the evolving landscape of technology - something rare to find in an agency.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":\"\",\"personsName\":\"Dave Kim\",\"jobTitle\":\"Producer Marketing Manager, Uber\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"761\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Made in Manhattan<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>With the location (New York) and the shops (Indie Fresh, Sam & Lex, and Ode \\u00e1 La Rose) locked in, we focused on producing a video that embodied the vim and vigor of Manhattan, using a quick cut editing style and visually following the goods en route from store to consumer. However, we made the video before the UberRUSH app existed, so we had to anticipate what it might look like and employ another app that would track users\\u2019 fingers on the screen. When the product was ready, we were able to attach it to the screen so that it was crisp and perfectly aligned with the video.<\\/p>\"}},\"741\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"734\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1019\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>A Bird\\u2019s Eye View<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We were also asked to include a lot of overhead shots in the production. To make it happen, we purchased a small camera jib and&mdash;with more than a little anxiety&mdash;we attached our $50K camera rig on top. Once the setup was secure, we were able to capture unique shots and enjoy the expanded possibilities of art direction and framing. <\\/p>\"}},\"742\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"743\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"730\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"745\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"728\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"744\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"740\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"755\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"752\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"756\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"753\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"757\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"754\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"971\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Payoff<\\/h1>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:23:14', '2017-10-24 17:23:14', '9b78c5dc-7af0-4847-8f33-da38a3b58cf6'),
 ('558', '672', '2', '75', 'en_us', '19', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Wealthfront\",\"slug\":\"wealthfront\",\"postDate\":1485990600,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Animating your journey to financial stability<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"725\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"958\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Financial management company Wealthfront offers software and apps to help people oversee their money in a straightforward way using robotic algorithms. Bokeh was brought on to make an informational animated video for the launch of Wealthfront\\u2019s new product, Path, a visual app that makes it easy for people to plan, track, and save for retirement. <\\/p>\"}},\"959\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Animated product launch video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"722\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/202971604\",\"caption\":\"Path by Wealthfront\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"717\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"712\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"960\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Wheel it out<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Wealthfront already had an illustration style and color palette in place on its site and wanted the video to fit that framework. Additionally, they asked us to convey a sense of active lifestyle. With these parameters, as well as the ultimate goal to convey the product information in an engaging way, we opted for a narrative centered on a woman biking&mdash;a metaphor for the ups and downs in life. We finessed the design to make sure it felt native to the existing site and used visual cues, such as increasingly expensive cars and larger homes, to illustrate the technical talking points in a lighthearted manner. <\\/p>\"}},\"720\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"723\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"961\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>This video was used in e-mail blast to Wealthfront\\u2019s vast audience of users to inform them about Path. This animation was also used on the main landing page for the dedicated Path website.<\\/p>\"}},\"721\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"714\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:23:32', '2017-10-24 17:23:32', '19f15c14-0a76-4df1-92dd-b390bc77b4f8'),
 ('559', '330', '2', '75', 'en_us', '20', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Play\",\"slug\":\"google-play\",\"postDate\":1491071400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#42e161\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Our parents thought this Google Play April Fool\'s joke was real. Success!<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"696\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"331\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The team at Google Play was certain about two things. First, they wanted a video to commemorate the April Fool\\u2019s holiday. Second, they wanted the video to involve pets. With these parameters outlined, Bokeh went to work to develop a hilarious and entertaining video to introduce <em>Google Play for Pets<\\/em>.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"332\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><li>Animation<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"654\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/213573065\",\"caption\":\"Google Play for Pets\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"333\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Make it believable<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We made the conscious decision to avoid cheap laughs and cute gimmicks; to create an April Fool\\u2019s video that took itself and its intent to lead the audience astray seriously. The story&mdash;and the product at its center&mdash;had to be grounded in a real-world logic that the viewer could \\u201calmost\\u201d follow. We needed to develop a product idea that was simple, and solved a real human issue.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our proposal: Google Play is introducing a new category of apps in the Play Store to help pet owners train their pets and keep them occupied while they\\u2019re away.<\\/p>\"}},\"953\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"655\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"658\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"644\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"657\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"634\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"659\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"643\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"661\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"635\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"662\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"651\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"656\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"641\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"334\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>With over 1.6M views across YouTube and Facebook, <em>Google Play for Pets <\\/em>was featured as one of the top April Fool\\u2019s pranks of 2017 by publications like <strong>Adweek<\\/strong> and <strong>CNET<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\"}},\"956\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"957\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"335\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cYou guys are literally amazing - thank you for dealing w\\/ this crazy last minute madness.\\\"\",\"avatar\":[\"773\"],\"personsName\":\"Meghan Lyons\",\"jobTitle\":\"Brand Marketing Manager, Google Play\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:24:24', '2017-10-24 17:24:24', '6262f62a-9a7c-4b40-9e68-7a4056f8a40d'),
 ('560', '341', '2', '75', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Maps\",\"slug\":\"google-maps\",\"postDate\":1430505420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#ffb500\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>The craziest damn video we\\u2019ve ever made for Google Maps in Turkey.<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"548\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"342\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To announce the launch of Google Streetview and the Google Maps mobile application in Turkey, Bokeh was asked to produce an inspiring anthem video. However, there was one hurdle: No map data or Streetview imagery would be accessible. To be successful, our stylistic approach had to be less reliant on the availability of digital imagery and more attached to the target market\\u2019s culture.<\\/p>\"}},\"554\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/130380842\",\"caption\":\"Google Maps: Hello Turkey\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"343\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Streetview minus the street view<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>How do you showcase a new feature without actually showing the feature? Establishing a partnership with DJI gave us the resources to shoot incredible aerial photography wherever we went. By combining this footage with hyperlapse photography and motion animation, we could mimic Satellite View in Google Maps and the user experience of moving between panoramas in Streetview.<\\/p>\"}},\"577\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/118982276\",\"caption\":\"Inspired by the DJI Inspire\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"344\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>From the Watchtower<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We reached out to Leonardo Dalessandri, the Italian director of the short film Watchtower of Turkey. Watchtower captured the essence of Turkish culture; a balanced, artistic survey of Turkey\\u2019s people, customs, food, and landscapes. The video had amassed millions of views within Turkey, and from a marketing perspective incorporating Leo\\u2019s aesthetic would establish an immediate point-of-reference for users. The awe-inspiring, kinetically entrancing nature of the approach combined with Google\\u2019s reach could give the video virality.<\\/p>\"}},\"555\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"558\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"542\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"557\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"549\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"559\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"544\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"560\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"545\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"561\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"552\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"345\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\\"This is super slick. Well done all around. Never seen anything quite like this\\u2026 The transitions between the various elements are so seamless.\\\"\",\"avatar\":[\"772\"],\"personsName\":\"Gopal Shah\",\"jobTitle\":\"Product Manager, Google Earth\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"346\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Hello Turkey<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Over the course of three weeks, we trekked across Istanbul and visited locales Izmir, Ephesus, \\u00c7e\\u015fme, and \\u015eirince.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"562\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"543\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"347\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Perhaps the most incredibly cinematic and dynamic Google Maps launch video ever made suffered the most anticlimactic of fates. Never formally released due to the political climate in Turkey.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"766\",\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', 'c6ee4c65-d649-4c83-8350-ebc24160ba9d'),
 ('561', '279', '2', '75', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"The Irvine Company\",\"slug\":\"the-irvine-company\",\"postDate\":1464744060,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#6e00af\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We made a video about real estate development exciting (Really.)<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"701\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"316\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>In 2016, residential real estate development and master planning company the Irvine Company asked Bokeh to create a series of videos to generate community excitement and encourage the Cupertino City Council to approve its latest development, The Hamptons, located adjacent to Apple Park.<\\/p>\"}},\"571\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/171478246\",\"caption\":\"The Hamptons, Cupertino\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"318\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Focus on What Really Matters<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Architects and developers aggrandizing another luxury development wasn\\u2019t going to resonate with anyone. In our interviews, we shifted the storytelling focus away from the specific design achievements of landscape architect Laurie Olin and architect Bernardo Fort-Brescia of Arquitectonica to how the development enriched the lives of its residents and the community of Cupertino as a whole. In other words, we felt the most effective approach would be to ground our story in humanity. <\\/p>\"}},\"572\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"573\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"702\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"574\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"700\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"575\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"699\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"576\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"703\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"319\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>See the Unseen<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To make a video for a development that didn\\u2019t exist yet, we partnered with the amazing creatives at Steelblue LLC to create 3D animated renderings of the complex with real and computer generated people in each space.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>First, they built out the CGI spaces with camera moves so we could make them consistent with the live-action shots. To make these homes feel active and alive, we asked Steelblue to fill up a green screen studio with a ton of extras. In fact, it was the most extras Steelblue had ever included in a single scene. It was also the first time they shot live extras swimming in a CGI pool. Using this combination of animation, interviews, aerial imagery, and B-roll footage, Bokeh made a real estate video with life and heart.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"868\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/174582836\",\"caption\":\"Green Screen Timelapse\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"320\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Cut-downs<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>It\\u2019s not easy to cover every detail of a multi-million dollar development in a single video. So we created a short series of topical cutdowns that highlighted The Hamptons\\u2019 most impressive features.<\\/p>\"}},\"578\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"579\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412289\",\"caption\":\"Sustainability\"}},\"580\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412287\",\"caption\":\"Planning Principles\"}},\"581\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412286\",\"caption\":\"Public Promenade\"}},\"582\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412285\",\"caption\":\"Building Composition\"}},\"583\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412284\",\"caption\":\"Perimeter Trail\"}},\"584\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412279\",\"caption\":\"Landscape\"}}}}},\"321\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Hallelujah Housing<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The Hamptons passed the city council and the master plan was approved. Hallelujah! We have housing.<\\/p>\"}},\"869\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"701\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"766\",\"358\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:26:23', '2017-10-24 17:26:23', '1b5b43a7-1a6c-4ce0-a3bd-33366016af60'),
 ('562', '77', '2', '75', 'en_us', '61', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Instagram for Business\",\"slug\":\"instagram\",\"postDate\":1503364800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#5188f5\",\"63\":[\"822\"],\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>We backpacked around the globe to shoot a series for<\\/strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\">Instagram<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"235\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"282\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>The Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram\\u2019s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.<\\/p>\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"458\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"459\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181711\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the UAE\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181279\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the United Kingdom\"}},\"461\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182109\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Germany\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193179905\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Spain\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975453\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Mexico\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975723\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Italy\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975916\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Brazil\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182537\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in France\"}}}}},\"323\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Nobody\\u2019s inspired by jargon<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, &nbsp;and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.<\\/p>\"}},\"467\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/153582145\",\"caption\":\"\\\"Made on Instagram\\\" Pitch Film\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"324\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Non-stop<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.<\\/p>\"}},\"492\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"498\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"29\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"493\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"432\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"494\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"470\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"490\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"488\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"707\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"706\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"711\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"710\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"325\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Breaking the Rules<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to \\u201caccidently\\u201d skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.<\\/p>\"}},\"499\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"497\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"326\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"bottom\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:28:44', '2017-10-24 17:28:44', '1033c67c-0180-4046-80cd-f7c4d08bb114'),
 ('563', '348', '2', '75', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Apple\",\"slug\":\"apple\",\"postDate\":1451846280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#87b0eb\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We did something for Apple.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"586\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"540\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"541\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:29:14', '2017-10-24 17:29:14', '54af5e83-4d37-4c16-9336-dfe9ace2c5a9'),
 ('564', '336', '2', '75', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb & Easyjet\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-easyjet\",\"postDate\":1470076380,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#e53f28\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>Airbnb wanted a boarding pass passengers wouldn\\u2019t just throw away<\\/strong><\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"691\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"337\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb noticed an interesting trend in Europe: A large percentage of Easyjet travellers are also avid Airbnb users. So in March 2017, Bokeh was asked to design a print ad to push Airbnb Experiences on the bottom third of all home-printed Easyjet boarding passes en route to Barcelona.<\\/p>\"}},\"338\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Make it Interactive<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The downside to boarding passes is that passengers just throw them away. For print-at-home boarding passes, little to no attention is paid to the lower quadrant of the page. Understandably, Airbnb did not want an ad with their logo to be ignored and dumped in the trash. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our thought process was simple: For Easyjet passengers, the lack of seat-back entertainment means that there are limited ways to stay occupied during a flight. What might capture their attention? A game. By playing a game, the passengers entertain themselves for five minutes and Airbnb is given five minutes of their attention. We decided to pitch a crossword puzzle.<\\/p>\"}},\"628\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"626\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"339\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Keep it simple<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We identified a list of words that related to Barcelona and some of the Experiences a traveller may partake in through Airbnb. We figured out how these words could fit together and came up with clues that were clever enough to keep the game fun, but easy enough to solve. (Safe to say, we went through many iterations.)<\\/p>\"}},\"340\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The final ad ran on over 200,000 boarding passes for all Easyjet flights to Barcelona from continental Europe during March 2017. <\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"313\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:29:35', '2017-10-24 17:29:35', '700124d1-b1da-47d8-b2ee-ec50c5e66feb'),
 ('565', '348', '2', '75', 'en_us', '15', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Apple\",\"slug\":\"apple\",\"postDate\":1446403080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#87b0eb\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We did something for Apple.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"586\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"540\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"541\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 17:30:21', '2017-10-24 17:30:21', 'b42fa295-aae2-478e-9ff2-986bbc2cc980'),
 ('566', '28', '2', '75', 'en_us', '56', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Philz Coffee\",\"slug\":\"philz-coffee\",\"postDate\":1502594280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#fd6300\",\"63\":[\"823\"],\"4\":\"<p>We cold called <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/philz-coffee#entry:28:url\\\">Philz Coffee<\\/a> to complain about their logo, and they let us do a rebrand.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"973\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"32\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Bokeh took the unconventional approach of exploring Philz\\u2019s brand identity, refreshing it, and sending a new brand deck directly to Philz\\u2019s CEO, Jacob Jaber. With custom coffee blends and a customer experience like no other, we felt that Philz deserved a brand it could fully own. The plan worked! Throughout the course of 2016, Bokeh worked intimately with the Philz team to define a uniform brand strategy that would serve as a guide for future growth. <\\/p>\"}},\"327\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Workshops<\\/li><li>Strategy<\\/li><li>Design<\\/li><li>Brand Book & Guidelines<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"1016\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1017\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"36\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"57\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"328\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Talk it Out<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Philz need a distinct vision, mission, and set of values that could be embraced internally and expressed in every decision they made. So after a romantic kick-off dinner we conducted individual interviews, a series of leadership workshops, and a company off-site to provide safe spaces to debate ideas and tinker with concepts. <\\/p>\"}},\"329\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Trippin\\u2019 on research<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>White-space exercises and market research helped us create a profile for the typical Philz customer and to understand the perception of the Philz brand compared to that of its competitors. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our research survey in San Francisco\\u2019s Bay Area, Los Angeles, and Washington, D.C. complemented the statistical analysis with in-person observations and on-site customer interviews.<\\/p>\"}},\"983\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1018\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1008\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"1011\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"998\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1010\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"997\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1012\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"999\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1013\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1000\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"33\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\\"The depth of each slide is quite impressive and on-point. I appreciate your quick-wittedness, intuition and aesthetic\\u2026 I think you know us better than we know ourselves.\\\"\",\"avatar\":[\"976\"],\"personsName\":\"Jacob Jaber\",\"jobTitle\":\"CEO\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"1007\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"993\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"985\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"984\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"981\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"975\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"50\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The style guide<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><em>Real<\\/em>, <em>warm<\\/em>, <em>undaunted<\\/em>, <em>relaxed<\\/em>, <em>neighborly<\\/em>, <em>light-hearted<\\/em>, and <em>unpretentious<\\/em> are the attributes infused throughout the new Philz brand identity. Starting with the logo and brand mark, we developed a custom system of colors, typography, illustrations, and iconography with guidelines.<\\/p>\"}},\"974\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"972\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1002\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"1003\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"991\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1004\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"989\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1005\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"992\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1006\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"990\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"979\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"978\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"987\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"986\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"51\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Philz chose to pace the launch of the new branding by starting with in-store menus, wayfinding signage, and promotional newsletters.<\\/p>\"}},\"1001\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"988\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"313\",\"314\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"center\"}}', '2017-10-24 18:30:37', '2017-10-24 18:30:37', 'b5132b76-a637-480b-9e71-242743524adc'),
