site to provide safe spaces to debate ideas and tinker with concepts. <\\/p>\"}},\"1024\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1022\"],\"caption\":\"CEO Jacob Jaber explores the feeling of screen printing a new Philz word mark.\"}},\"329\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Trippin\\u2019 on research<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>White-space exercises and market research helped us create a profile for the typical Philz customer and to understand the perception of the Philz brand compared to that of its competitors. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our research survey in San Francisco\\u2019s Bay Area, Los Angeles, and Washington, D.C. complemented the statistical analysis with in-person observations and on-site customer interviews.<\\/p>\"}},\"983\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1018\"],\"caption\":\"Survey-takers were asked to imagine Philz, Starbucks, Peet\'s and Blue Bottle as a person. In their responses, we identified the quintessential traits that make Philz customers unique.\"}},\"1008\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"1011\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"998\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1010\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"997\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1012\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"999\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1013\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1000\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"33\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\\"The depth of each slide is quite impressive and on-point. I appreciate your quick-wittedness, intuition and aesthetic\\u2026 I think you know us better than we know ourselves.\\\"\",\"avatar\":[\"976\"],\"personsName\":\"Jacob Jaber\",\"jobTitle\":\"CEO\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"1007\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"993\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"985\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":