 ('580', '1028', '2', '75', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Citizen\",\"slug\":\"citizen\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#000000\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video about student aid that we wish we had growing up<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":\"\",\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Citizen is an online tool that helps students fill out the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA), turning the complicated task of filling out government forms into a streamlined process with easy-to-understand questions. The start-up wanted a video that was both an overview and a tutorial, a request that required some creative visuals to make the dry information compelling. <\\/p>\\r\\n\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Service<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Animation<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Here\\u2019s Looking at You, Kid<\\/h1><p>The creative was open-ended, so we crafted a fun animation of a teenage girl and her mother applying for FAFSA with demonstrations of Citizen embedded throughout. The overview gave us a chance to bring the video to life with our teenage narrator, while the tutorial aspect walks the viewer through product screens to show how it is used. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To help the client meet a tight budget, we did the animation in-house. This gave us the opportunity to drop a few Easter eggs (namely, cats), throughout the video, from felines in different rooms of the story to a \\u201c Go Wildcats\\u201d banner in the school. <\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 22:48:10', '2017-10-24 22:48:10', 'a050b2d4-e054-465c-81b8-fa3db24f9393'),
 ('581', '682', '2', '75', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UberRUSH\",\"slug\":\"uberrush\",\"postDate\":1438470840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We helped Uber make a video to announce their newest service: UberRUSH<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"726\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"760\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1><strong>Mission<\\/strong><\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Uber hired Bokeh to make the launch film for UberRUSH, which uses its network of drivers and bicycle couriers to pick up and deliver items from stores and retailers that don\\u2019t offer courier services. UberRUSH would launch in New York first, so we used the city as our backdrop and focused on three deliverable areas: food (Indie Fresh, a mason jar meal company), clothing ( Sam & Lex, an upscale boutique) and flowers (Ode \\u00e1 La Rose, a flower shop).<\\/p>\"}},\"759\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"727\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/138801682\",\"caption\":\"UberRush, Your On-Demand Network\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"746\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"747\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"731\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"748\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"737\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"749\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"729\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"750\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"736\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"751\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"735\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"825\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cI\\u2019ve worked with Bokeh on a number of projects. They consistently deliver beautiful content while remaining extremely agile in dealing with the evolving landscape of technology - something rare to find in an agency.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":\"\",\"personsName\":\"Dave Kim\",\"jobTitle\":\"Producer Marketing Manager, Uber\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"761\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Made in Manhattan<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>With the location (New York) and the shops (Indie Fresh, Sam & Lex, and Ode \\u00e1 La Rose) locked in, we focused on producing a video that embodied the vim and vigor of Manhattan, using a quick cut editing style and visually following the goods en route from store to consumer. However, we made the video before the UberRUSH app existed, so we had to anticipate what it might look like and employ another app that would track users\\u2019 fingers on the screen. When the product was ready, we were able to attach it to the screen so that it was crisp and perfectly aligned with the video.<\\/p>\"}},\"741\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"734\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1019\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>A Bird\\u2019s Eye View<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We were also asked to include a lot of overhead shots in the production. To make it happen, we purchased a small camera jib and&mdash;with more than a little anxiety&mdash;we attached our $50K camera rig on top. Once the setup was secure, we were able to capture unique shots and enjoy the expanded possibilities of art direction and framing. <\\/p>\"}},\"742\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"743\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"730\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"745\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"728\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"744\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"740\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"755\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"752\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"756\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"753\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"757\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"754\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"971\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Payoff<\\/h1>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1032\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 22:49:59', '2017-10-24 22:49:59', 'bc365011-14a8-4afa-8b18-227d4dff2e6c'),
