he school. <\\/p>\"}},\"1043\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"1044\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1039\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1045\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1038\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1046\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1042\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1047\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1041\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1048\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1040\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1049\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1037\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 23:41:52', '2017-10-24 23:41:52', 'ba1cd594-d38b-472b-a97c-a90b5ebe2e47'),
 ('589', '279', '2', '75', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"The Irvine Company\",\"slug\":\"the-irvine-company\",\"postDate\":1464744060,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#6e00af\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We made a video about real estate development exciting (Really.)<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"701\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"316\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>In 2016, residential real estate development and master planning company the Irvine Company asked Bokeh to create a series of videos to generate community excitement and encourage the Cupertino City Council to approve its latest development, The Hamptons, located adjacent to Apple Park.<\\/p>\"}},\"571\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/171478246\",\"caption\":\"The Hamptons, Cupertino\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"318\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Focus on What Really Matters<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Architects and developers aggrandizing another luxury development wasn\\u2019t going to resonate with anyone. In our interviews, we shifted the storytelling focus away from the specific design achievements of landscape architect Laurie Olin and architect Bernardo Fort-Brescia of Arquitectonica to how the development enriched the lives of its residents and the community of Cupertino as a whole. In other words, we felt the most effective approach would be to ground our story in humanity. <\\/p>\"}},\"572\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"573\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"702\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"574\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"700\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"575\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"699\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"576\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"703\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"319\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>See the Unseen<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To make a video for a development that didn\\u2019t exist yet, we partnered with the amazing creatives at Steelblue LLC to create 3D animated renderings of the complex with real and computer generated people in each space.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>First, they built out the CGI spaces with camera moves so we could make them consistent with the live-action shots. To make these homes feel active and alive, we asked Steelblue to fill up a green screen studio with a ton of extras. In fact, it was the most extras Steelblue had ever included in a single scene. It was also the first time they shot live extras swimming in a CGI pool. Using this combination of animation, interviews, aerial imagery, and B-roll footage, Bokeh made a real estate video with life and heart.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"868\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/174582836\",\"caption\":\"Green Screen Timelapse\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"320\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Cut-downs<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>It\\u2019s not easy to cover every detail of a multi-million dollar development in a single video. So we created a short series of topical cutdowns that highlighted The Hamptons\\u2019 most impressive features.<\\/p>\"}},\"578\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"579\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412289\",\"caption\":\"Sustainability\"}},\"580\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412287\",\"caption\":\"Planning Principles\"}},\"581\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412286\",\"caption\":\"Public Promenade\"}},\"582\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412285\",\"caption\":\"Building Composition\"}},\"583\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412284\",\"caption\":\"Perimeter Trail\"}},\"584\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/168412279\",\"caption\":\"Landscape\"}}}}},\"321\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Hallelujah Housing<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The Hamptons passed the city council and the master plan was approved. Hallelujah! We have housing.<\\/p>\"}},\"869\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"701\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', '1a23cae0-dffd-4bde-9af2-0c704b7a20b5'),
 ('590', '77', '2', '75', 'en_us', '62', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Instagram for Business\",\"slug\":\"instagram\",\"postDate\":1503364800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#5188f5\",\"63\":[\"822\"],\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>We backpacked around the globe to shoot a series for<\\/strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\">Instagram<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"235\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"282\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>The Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram\\u2019s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.<\\/p>\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"458\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"459\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181711\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the UAE\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181279\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the United Kingdom\"}},\"461\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182109\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Germany\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193179905\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Spain\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975453\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Mexico\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975723\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Italy\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975916\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Brazil\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182537\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in France\"}}}}},\"323\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Nobody\\u2019s inspired by jargon<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, &nbsp;and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.<\\/p>\"}},\"467\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/153582145\",\"caption\":\"\\\"Made on Instagram\\\" Pitch Film\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"324\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Non-stop<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.<\\/p>\"}},\"492\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"498\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"29\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"493\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"432\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"494\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"470\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"490\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"488\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"711\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"710\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"325\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Breaking the Rules<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to \\u201caccidently\\u201d skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.<\\/p>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1053\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"499\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"497\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"326\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"bottom\"}}', '2017-10-24 23:46:30', '2017-10-24 23:46:30', 'e056ad0a-41e0-473b-bf40-16f578719c91'),
 ('591', '77', '2', '75', 'en_us', '63', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Instagram for Business\",\"slug\":\"instagram\",\"postDate\":1503364800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#5188f5\",\"63\":[\"822\"],\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>We backpacked around the globe to shoot a series for<\\/strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\">Instagram<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"235\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"282\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>The Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram\\u2019s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.<\\/p>\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"458\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"459\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181711\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the UAE\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181279\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the United Kingdom\"}},\"461\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182109\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Germany\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193179905\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Spain\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975453\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Mexico\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975723\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Italy\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975916\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Brazil\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182537\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in France\"}}}}},\"323\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Nobody\\u2019s inspired by jargon<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, &nbsp;and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.<\\/p>\"}},\"467\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/153582145\",\"caption\":\"\\\"Made on Instagram\\\" Pitch Film\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"324\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Non-stop<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.<\\/p>\"}},\"492\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"498\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"29\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"493\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"432\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"494\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"470\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"490\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"488\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"711\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"710\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"325\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Breaking the Rules<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to \\u201caccidently\\u201d skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.<\\/p>\"}},\"499\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"497\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1054\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1055\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"326\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"bottom\"}}', '2017-10-24 23:48:30', '2017-10-24 23:48:30', '1ed35fc9-dcaa-4b0b-8486-0f0120e3718d'),
 ('592', '762', '2', '75', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb Vacation Rentals\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-vacation-rentals\",\"postDate\":1507497960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#ee8108\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We told a story the vacation rentals community could own for <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-vacation-rentals#entry:762:url\\\">Airbnb<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"892\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"763\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb cofounder and CSO Nathan Blecharczyk was a keynote speaker at the Vacation Rental Managers Association national conference in Orlando, Florida. Airbnb tasked Bokeh with creating a video that conveyed Airbnb\\u2019s brand values of human connection and empathy.<\\/p>\"}},\"905\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/239024086\",\"caption\":\"Yonder & Airbnb | Building Memorable Experiences Together\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"764\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Not just passing through<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb has been somewhat of a dark horse in the vacation rental community and Nathan\\u2019s presentation needed to recognize that issue and connect to potential new hosts. As part of that ambition, we opted for a documentary-style film that told the story of a host and his business without relying on Airbnb talking points.<\\/p>\"}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"928\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>We found Steve Frellick of Yonder Luxury Home Rentals in Asheville, North Carolina. Steve was on the brink of foreclosure during the recession of 2008 when his bank asked him to convert the family home he built into a vacation rental. Today, Yonder manages over 80 properties throughout North and South Carolina.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Steve\\u2019s story not only encapsulates an inherently American narrative, but his humility, passion, and empathy for his guests aligned his approach with Airbnb\\u2019s ethos of seeking common interests and forging connections. As a native of North Carolina, we felt Steve\\u2019s story would resonate with an audience in Orlando, many of whom were from the Southeast and lived through the Great Recession themselves.<\\/p>\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"937\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"899\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"938\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"893\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"939\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"890\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"940\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"885\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"941\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"878\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"942\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"879\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"765\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Early birds<\\/h1><p>Airbnb is all about interaction, but a big part of Yonder\\u2019s success comes from keeping interaction with guests to a minimum. Yonder\'s there to make check-in seamless and to provide guidance as needed, but fundamentally wants guests to unwind in their homes without interruption. To remedy this, we focussed the narrative on Steve\\u2019s relationship to his homes and surroundings. We captured moments of interaction with his business partner at a local diner, and accompanied him to one of his favorite places, the baseball diamond.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>We also woke up early to capture the natural beauty of Asheville and the Great Smoky Mountains. The morning fog spread out like stretched cotton and caressed the treetops. Lying gently between the folds of quiet valleys as if to hide from the sun for an extra 5 minutes. These sunrise hikes and drone photography shoots allowed us to give Steve and his homes context in their environment. It also gave us a true sense for why people call North Carolina \\u201chome\\u201d.\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"932\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"359\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:25:12', '2017-10-25 17:25:12', '48080b72-e365-4740-af40-81fc7087c8c5'),
 ('593', '762', '2', '75', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Airbnb Vacation Rentals\",\"slug\":\"airbnb-vacation-rentals\",\"postDate\":1507497960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#ee8108\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We told a story the vacation rentals community could own for <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb-vacation-rentals#entry:762:url\\\">Airbnb<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"892\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"763\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb cofounder and CSO Nathan Blecharczyk was a keynote speaker at the Vacation Rental Managers Association national conference in Orlando, Florida. Airbnb tasked Bokeh with creating a video that conveyed Airbnb\\u2019s brand values of human connection and empathy.<\\/p>\"}},\"905\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/239024086\",\"caption\":\"Yonder & Airbnb | Building Memorable Experiences Together\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"764\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Not just passing through<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb has been somewhat of a dark horse in the vacation rental community and Nathan\\u2019s presentation needed to recognize that issue and connect to potential new hosts. As part of that ambition, we opted for a documentary-style film that told the story of a host and his business without relying on Airbnb talking points.<\\/p>\"}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"928\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>We found Steve Frellick of Yonder Luxury Home Rentals in Asheville, North Carolina. Steve was on the brink of foreclosure during the recession of 2008 when his bank asked him to convert the family home he built into a vacation rental. Today, Yonder manages over 80 properties throughout North and South Carolina.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Steve\\u2019s story not only encapsulates an inherently American narrative, but his humility, passion, and empathy for his guests aligned his approach with Airbnb\\u2019s ethos of seeking common interests and forging connections. As a native of North Carolina, we felt Steve\\u2019s story would resonate with an audience in Orlando, many of whom were from the Southeast and lived through the Great Recession themselves.<\\/p>\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"937\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"899\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"938\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"893\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"939\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"890\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"940\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"885\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"941\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"878\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"942\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"879\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"765\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Early birds<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Airbnb is all about interaction, but a big part of Yonder\\u2019s success comes from keeping interaction with guests to a minimum. Yonder\'s there to make check-in seamless and to provide guidance as needed, but fundamentally wants guests to unwind in their homes without interruption. To remedy this, we focussed the narrative on Steve\\u2019s relationship to his homes and surroundings. We captured moments of interaction with his business partner at a local diner, and accompanied him to one of his favorite places, the baseball diamond.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We also woke up early to capture the natural beauty of Asheville and the Great Smoky Mountains. The morning fog spread out like stretched cotton and caressed the treetops. Lying gently between the folds of quiet valleys as if to hide from the sun for an extra 5 minutes. These sunrise hikes and drone photography shoots allowed us to give Steve and his homes context in their environment. It also gave us a true sense for why people call North Carolina \\u201chome\\u201d.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"932\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"359\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', '01552239-50e8-4dc5-bfb6-e562b20f68be'),
 ('594', '767', '2', '75', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Local Guides\",\"slug\":\"google-local-guides\",\"postDate\":1441144380,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#f4ac1b\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>We did a Photo-Worthy Photoshoot for Google <\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"779\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"768\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Google Local Guides is a program where users leave reviews and upload photos of their favorite places so that others can find and experience them too. In September 2015, we were asked to conceptualize and produce bright and colorful photography that spoke to the values at the heart of the Local Guides brand&mdash;discovery, sharing, community. The final images would be incorporated into the Google Local Guides microsite.<\\/p>\"}},\"809\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"807\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mocking the microsite<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>As part of the conceptualization process, we were tasked with envisioning the user experience on desktop and mobile devices in order to recommend approaches for the UX\\/UI design of the Local Guides microsite. This meant that our photography needed to work across platforms in both vertical and horizontal orientations. To ensure our images did that, we built out wireframe mockups of the website.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}},\"769\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Location, location, location<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We started by identifying the cool local places that would resonate most with millennials (i.e. us.). We wanted to show spots slightly off the beaten path that people would be genuinely excited to share. The final list included places such as Pizzeria Delfina, Shark Fin Cove, Philz, the Santa Cruz Beach Boardwalk, and Chantal Guillon Macarons.<\\/p>\"}},\"771\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Payoff<\\/h1>\"}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"803\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"815\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"802\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"811\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"813\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"812\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"810\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}}},\"2\":[\"766\",\"359\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:36:01', '2017-10-25 17:36:01', '8b5addad-4e51-4a9b-8552-c7b56a9cae29'),
 ('595', '330', '2', '75', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Google Play\",\"slug\":\"google-play\",\"postDate\":1491071400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#42e161\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Our parents thought this Google Play April Fool\'s joke was real. Success!<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"696\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"331\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The team at Google Play was certain about two things. First, they wanted a video to commemorate the April Fool\\u2019s holiday. Second, they wanted the video to involve pets. With these parameters outlined, Bokeh went to work to develop a hilarious and entertaining video to introduce <em>Google Play for Pets<\\/em>.<br><\\/p>\"}},\"332\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><li>Animation<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"654\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/213573065\",\"caption\":\"Google Play for Pets\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"333\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Make it believable<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We made the conscious decision to avoid cheap laughs and cute gimmicks; to create an April Fool\\u2019s video that took itself and its intent to lead the audience astray seriously. The story&mdash;and the product at its center&mdash;had to be grounded in a real-world logic that the viewer could \\u201calmost\\u201d follow. We needed to develop a product idea that was simple, and solved a real human issue.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our proposal: Google Play is introducing a new category of apps in the Play Store to help pet owners train their pets and keep them occupied while they\\u2019re away.<\\/p>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>C\\u2019mon get appy<\\/h1><p>To start, we needed to bring the joke home by dreaming up with an assortment of Play for Pets apps that were believable enough for people to look up. After creating all of the animal puns we could muster, we designed a new series of fun app icons to match. <\\/p>\"}},\"953\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Cat-ing Call<\\/h1><p>In perhaps our most unusual casting call yet, we asked Google employees (Googlers) to lend their pets and personalities to the production. While we had plenty of Dooglers apply, we made a special effort to include \\u201cactors\\u201d of all kinds, including Altair the turtle, Pom Pom the chinchilla, and Noodle the chicken (an absolute primadonna).<\\/p>\"}},\"655\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"658\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"644\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"657\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"634\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"659\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"643\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"661\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"635\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"662\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"651\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"656\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"641\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"334\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>With over 1.6M views across YouTube and Facebook, <em>Google Play for Pets <\\/em>was featured as one of the top April Fool\\u2019s pranks of 2017 by publications like <strong>Adweek<\\/strong> and <strong>CNET<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\"}},\"956\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"957\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"335\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cYou guys are literally amazing - thank you for dealing w\\/ this crazy last minute madness.\\\"\",\"avatar\":[\"773\"],\"personsName\":\"Meghan Lyons\",\"jobTitle\":\"Brand Marketing Manager, Google Play\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:44:27', '2017-10-25 17:44:27', 'c9fd6711-77c9-4d4e-b1e8-1257858358ab'),
 ('596', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1433545740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0092ff\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video shot around the world without leaving our office<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"970\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"964\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The video\\u2019s message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. <\\/p>\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Stock up<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.<\\/p>\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Compose Yourself<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To amp up the video\\u2019s emotional impact, we needed a score that would touch hearts. We fell in love with the music (and name) of Icelandic composer J\\u00f3hann J\\u00f3hannsson, who had recently been nominated for an Oscar nomination for <i>The Theory of Everything<\\/i>. We reached out to him and persuaded him to donate his talents to saving the world (he agreed). <\\/p>\"}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New York\\u2019s Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEP\\u2019s displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.<\\/p>\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"Our video played in New York\'s Time Square.\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:47:46', '2017-10-25 17:47:46', 'f20e1462-500f-45f9-8cb9-4268cb589af7'),
 ('597', '671', '2', '75', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UNEP\",\"slug\":\"united-nations-environment-programe\",\"postDate\":1433545740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#0092ff\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>We made a video shot around the world without leaving our office<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"970\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"964\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The video\\u2019s message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. <\\/p>\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/129727110\",\"caption\":\"Seven Billion Dreams. One Planet. Consume with Care - UNEP World Environment Day\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Stock up<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.<\\/p>\"}},\"1059\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Compose Yourself<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To amp up the video\\u2019s emotional impact, we needed a score that would touch hearts. We fell in love with the music (and name) of Icelandic composer J\\u00f3hann J\\u00f3hannsson, who had recently been nominated for an Oscar nomination for <em>The Theory of Everything<\\/em>. We reached out to him and persuaded him to donate his talents to saving the world (he agreed). <\\/p>\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"687\"],\"caption\":\"Our video played in New York\'s Time Square.\"}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New York\\u2019s Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEP\\u2019s displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:48:17', '2017-10-25 17:48:17', '78914af2-48d9-4b8f-87ac-f12ca99b1153'),
 ('598', '672', '2', '75', 'en_us', '20', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Wealthfront\",\"slug\":\"wealthfront\",\"postDate\":1485990600,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>Animating your journey to financial stability<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"725\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"958\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Financial management company Wealthfront offers software and apps to help people oversee their money in a straightforward way using robotic algorithms. Bokeh was brought on to make an informational animated video for the launch of Wealthfront\\u2019s new product, Path, a visual app that makes it easy for people to plan, track, and save for retirement. <\\/p>\"}},\"722\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/202971604\",\"caption\":\"Path by Wealthfront\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"960\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Wheel it out<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Wealthfront already had an illustration style and color palette in place on its site and wanted the video to fit that framework. Additionally, they asked us to convey a sense of active lifestyle. With these parameters, as well as the ultimate goal to make the product information engaging, we opted for a narrative centered around a female bicyclist&mdash;a metaphor for the ups and downs in life. We finessed the design to make sure it felt native to the existing site and used visual cues, such as increasingly expensive cars and larger homes, to illustrate the technical talking points in a lighthearted manner.  <\\/p>\"}},\"717\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"712\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"720\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"723\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"961\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>This video was used in e-mail blast to Wealthfront\\u2019s vast audience of users to inform them about Path. This animation was also used on the main landing page for the dedicated Path website.<\\/p>\"}},\"721\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"714\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"350\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 17:54:20', '2017-10-25 17:54:20', '45c5d7a7-1d99-45d7-be2b-56615b62593f'),
 ('599', '682', '2', '75', 'en_us', '26', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"UberRUSH\",\"slug\":\"uberrush\",\"postDate\":1438470840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#00b4ae\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>The launch video for UberRUSH was true to its namesake. What a rush!<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"726\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"760\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1><strong>The Mission<\\/strong><\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>UberRUSH uses Uber\\u2019s network of drivers and bicycle couriers to pick up and deliver items from stores and retailers that don\\u2019t offer delivery. Launching in New York, we used the city as our backdrop and focused on three delivery categories: food (Indie Fresh, a mason jar meal company), clothing (Sam & Lex, an upscale boutique) and flowers (Ode \\u00e1 La Rose, a flower shop).<\\/p>\"}},\"759\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Services<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"727\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/138801682\",\"caption\":\"UberRush, Your On-Demand Network\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"746\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"747\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"731\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"748\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"737\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"749\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"729\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"750\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"736\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"751\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"735\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"825\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cI\\u2019ve worked with Bokeh on a number of projects. They consistently deliver beautiful content while remaining extremely agile in dealing with the evolving landscape of technology - something rare to find in an agency.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":\"\",\"personsName\":\"Dave Kim\",\"jobTitle\":\"Producer Marketing Manager, Uber\",\"shapeBackground\":[\"show\"]}},\"761\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Made in Manhattan<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>With the location (New York) and the shops (Indie Fresh, Sam & Lex, and Ode \\u00e1 La Rose) locked in, our creative attention went toward infusing our video with the vim and vigor of Manhattan. Our narrative followed goods en route from store to customer while employing a quick cut editing style that built momentum.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The one rub: the UberRUSH app was not ready by the start of physical production. So we anticipated user interactions and then used a green screen app to track the finger movements of our actors. When the product was built, we were able to easily attach it to the screen so that the UI was visually crisp and perfectly aligned.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"}},\"741\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"734\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1019\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>A Bird\\u2019s Eye View<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>We decided to include a lot of overhead shots in the production. To make it happen, we purchased a small camera jib and&mdash;with more than a little anxiety&mdash;we attached our $50K camera rig on top. Once the setup was secure, we were able to capture unique shots and enjoy the expanded possibilities of art direction and framing. <\\/p>\"}},\"742\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"743\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"730\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"745\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"728\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"744\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"740\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"755\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"752\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"756\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"753\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"757\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"754\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"971\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Payoff<\\/h1>\"}},\"1033\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1032\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 18:21:09', '2017-10-25 18:21:09', 'ebfdd639-fdc4-4704-9c80-a6f733088adc'),
 ('600', '1028', '2', '75', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Citizen\",\"slug\":\"citizen\",\"postDate\":1464823560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#2c3971\",\"63\":\"\",\"4\":\"<p>It would have been nice to have Citizen back when we were filling out FAFSAs.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"left\",\"3\":[\"1036\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"1029\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The Mission<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Citizen is an online tool that helps students fill out the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA), turning the complicated task of filling out government forms into a streamlined process with easy-to-understand questions. The start-up needed a video that could serve as an overview and a tutorial. It would require some creative visuals to make this dry information compelling. <\\/p>\"}},\"1030\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Service<\\/h1>\\r\\n<ul><li>Animation<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"1035\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/154131379\",\"caption\":\"Citizen FAFSA\",\"ratio\":\"16-9\"}},\"1051\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1052\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1031\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Here\\u2019s Looking at You, Kid<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>To introduce Citizen, we crafted a story around a teenage girl and her mother applying for FAFSA. The teenager served as our narrator. Balancing an appropriate amount of story alongside UI demonstrations allowed us to showcase Citizen\\u2019s product while aligning the perspective of the video with that of Citizen\\u2019s target demographic.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Of course, it\\u2019s not a Bokeh animation unless we throw in a few Easter eggs (namely, cats). From placing felines in different scenes to a \\u201c Go Wildcats\\u201d banner in the school, our motion designer may have gone a bit kitty-crazy.<span><\\/span><\\/p><p> <\\/p>\"}},\"1043\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"1044\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1039\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1045\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1038\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1046\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1042\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1047\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1041\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1048\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1040\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1049\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1037\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}}},\"2\":[\"350\",\"313\"],\"9\":\"top\"}}', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', '009b8d7d-cc87-4e8a-908b-1307bd27d938'),
 ('601', '77', '2', '75', 'en_us', '64', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Instagram for Business\",\"slug\":\"instagram\",\"postDate\":1503364800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#5188f5\",\"63\":[\"822\"],\"4\":\"<p><strong><strong>We backpacked around the globe to shoot a series for<\\/strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/instagram#entry:77:url\\\">Instagram<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"235\"],\"5\":\"\",\"10\":{\"282\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>The Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram\\u2019s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.<\\/p>\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>Services<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul><li>Concept<\\/li><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Film\\/Video<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"458\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"459\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181711\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the UAE\"}},\"460\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193181279\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in the United Kingdom\"}},\"461\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182109\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Germany\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193179905\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Spain\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975453\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Mexico\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975723\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Italy\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/197975916\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in Brazil\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193182537\",\"caption\":\"Global Spotlight: Instagram in France\"}}}}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1060\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"323\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Nobody\\u2019s inspired by jargon<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, &nbsp;and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.<\\/p>\"}},\"467\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/153582145\",\"caption\":\"\\\"Made on Instagram\\\" Pitch Film\",\"ratio\":\"235-1\"}},\"324\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Non-stop<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.<\\/p>\"}},\"492\":{\"type\":\"imageCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":{\"498\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"29\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"493\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"432\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"494\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"470\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"490\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"488\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"711\":{\"type\":\"2\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"710\"],\"caption\":\"\"}}}}},\"325\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>Breaking the Rules<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to \\u201caccidently\\u201d skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.<\\/p>\"}},\"499\":{\"type\":\"inlineImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"497\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"1054\":{\"type\":\"fullWidthImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"1055\"],\"caption\":\"\"}},\"326\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h1>The payoff<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.<\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"322\",\"350\",\"766\"],\"9\":\"bottom\"}}', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', '0e0a84d0-af0c-4afc-9bc0-fa1e3d798ba7'),
