INSERT INTO `craft_matrixcontent_projectblocks` (`id`, `elementId`, `locale`, `field_text_copy`, `field_quote_quote`, `field_quote_personsName`, `field_quote_jobTitle`, `field_video_videoUrl`, `field_video_caption`, `field_inlineImage_caption`, `field_fullWidthImage_caption`, `field_quote_shapeBackground`, `field_video_ratio`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES
 ('1', '32', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>Bokeh took the unconventional approach of exploring Philzs brand identity, refreshing it, and sending a new brand deck directly to Philzs CEO, Jacob Jaber. With custom coffee blends and a customer experience like no other, we felt that Philz deserved a brand it could fully own. The plan worked! Throughout the course of 2016, Bokeh worked intimately with the Philz team to define a uniform brand strategy that would serve as a guide for future growth. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 00:40:09', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'e131a475-d304-4e6f-b770-3c084d70199b'),
 ('2', '33', 'en_us', NULL, '\"The depth of each slide is quite impressive and on-point. I appreciate your quick-wittedness, intuition and aesthetic I think you know us better than we know ourselves.\"', 'Jacob Jaber', 'CEO', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', NULL, '2017-08-20 00:40:09', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '2a264b89-91fd-4abd-85fa-dee39f1f5e4b'),
 ('5', '36', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 00:40:09', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'c53c7634-6616-426f-9f9b-a18a29d65140'),
 ('11', '50', 'en_us', '<h1>The style guide</h1>\n<p><em>Real</em>, <em>warm</em>, <em>undaunted</em>, <em>relaxed</em>, <em>neighborly</em>, <em>light-hearted</em>, and <em>unpretentious</em> are the attributes infused throughout the new Philz brand identity. Starting with the logo and brand mark, we developed a custom system of colors, typography, illustrations, and iconography with guidelines.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '5635f71e-d722-40d4-8244-b62213e01369'),
 ('12', '51', 'en_us', '<h1>The payoff</h1>\n<p>Philz chose to pace the launch of the new branding by starting with in-store menus, wayfinding signage, and promotional newsletters.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'a0d2adf0-bbff-4d32-ba9e-375b734b10bc'),
 ('18', '146', 'en_us', NULL, 'This film brought the house down. I cannot imagine now having done this without it.', 'Brian Chesky', 'CEO of Airbnb', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', NULL, '2017-08-30 22:22:29', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', 'fd1caad1-c016-4dc2-aa9d-2f3f07b0a960'),
 ('19', '147', 'en_us', '<h2>The Mission</h2>\n<p>On November 17, 2016, Airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history. Just five weeks earlier, Bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line.</p>\n<p>Working alongside engineering, brand, product marketing, art, and C-level teams, we developed myriad content to educate users on new features, advertise and build awareness on social media, and, ultimately, to introduce the world to Airbnb Trips on-stage at Airbnb Open in Los Angeles.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:22:29', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', 'e6a84c3b-efcb-4050-be6b-0b7b35d592ab'),
 ('21', '153', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/193175968', 'Welcome to the World of Trips | Aired During Airbnb Open 2016 Keynote', NULL, NULL, NULL, '16-9', '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '90203f47-8e08-4281-a3b5-d4bc8c975926'),
 ('23', '155', 'en_us', '<h2>Lets get functional</h2>\n<p>Humanity is a core component of the Airbnb brand. Every feature and service built into the new Airbnb app derives value from the way it connects to guests, hosts, and experiences. To reinforce this connection, we melded organic live-action footage with engaging UI animations and garnished it all with a touch of whimsy. The result was twelve functional product videos viewable in landscape and portrait mode.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '27768f68-29a0-4b9a-8465-fa374eff403d'),
 ('25', '157', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '13670490-8b75-4497-9cae-184eafd6198f'),
 ('26', '162', 'en_us', '<h2>The Reveal</h2>\n<p>With two days before Airbnb Open, Brian needed a Hail Mary. He lacked a centerpiece for the launch announcement that firmly connected Airbnbs digital product with the human experiences it fosters. So he asked us to apply our creative approach to the keynote anthem and make a film about the future of home sharing.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', 'ae394f81-86c0-4131-9a6e-577349ef6453'),
 ('29', '165', 'en_us', '<h2>Marketing Master Blaster</h2>\n<p>To build awareness, we applied this approach to four 15-second advertisements blasted across digital and social channels.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '35f1a283-1e27-424e-8b82-efd24bade08d'),
 ('30', '166', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/193184792', 'Airbnb Collections Teaser | Aired During AO 2016 Keynote', NULL, NULL, NULL, '235-1', '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '792b8428-a6dc-4e12-aacc-b2b2667b7677'),
 ('31', '167', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '485d0d4e-e8d2-4424-b42e-6ccd7af64f96'),
 ('33', '179', 'en_us', '<h2>The payoff</h2>\n<p>The assets were leveraged across a variety of channels from Airbnb Open to product landing pages, social and YouTube, email newsletters, and paid media. The functional videos amassed over <strong>11 million views</strong><strong> in less than three weeks</strong>. On Airbnb product pages, the <strong>video click-through-rate reached as high as 15 percent</strong>. </p>\n<p>We received coverage in the <strong><em>NYTimes</em></strong><strong>, Adweek, </strong><strong><em>Travel + Leisure</em></strong><strong>, TechCrunch, Mashable, </strong><strong><em>The Telegraph</em></strong><strong>, and Fast Company.</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:42:57', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '560e4036-cd0d-487f-bbaa-6abdf3e73e45'),
 ('35', '181', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:42:57', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '57e43956-a26f-45c5-846a-588677927cda'),
 ('37', '251', 'en_us', '<h2>Services</h2>\n<ul><li>Concept</li><li>Branding Animation</li><li>Film/Video</li><li>Animation</li><li>Digital Ads</li><li>Social Ads</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-14 00:40:35', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '7150841f-82bb-4947-9659-8b98a3b5cf3c'),
 ('39', '281', 'en_us', '<h2>The bow on top</h2>\n<p>Every piece of content featured a reimagined Airbnb motion logo consistent with the fluid design aesthetic we developed for our animations.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-26 01:36:37', '2017-10-09 00:25:34', '24824216-fea5-4407-acaa-cb2dfe1c4a2e'),
 ('40', '282', 'en_us', '<h2>The Mission</h2>\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagrams top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-26 01:47:21', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'd74246e0-e4d6-44b7-821e-2531203656e0'),
 ('41', '283', 'en_us', '<h2>Services</h2>\n<ul><li>Concept</li><li>Branding</li><li>Film/Video</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-26 01:47:21', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'dbb9b474-15af-439d-a220-9e3034ba7ef5'),
 ('42', '316', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>In 2016, residential real estate development and master planning company the Irvine Company asked Bokeh to create a series of videos to generate community excitement and encourage the Cupertino City Council to approve its latest development, The Hamptons, located adjacent to Apple Park.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-02 20:40:39', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', 'e24320ee-f143-4b5c-8647-391e62a8b70a'),
 ('43', '318', 'en_us', '<h1>Focus on What Really Matters</h1>\n<p>Architects and developers aggrandizing another luxury development wasnt going to resonate with anyone. In our interviews, we shifted the storytelling focus away from the specific design achievements of landscape architect Laurie Olin and architect Bernardo Fort-Brescia of Arquitectonica to how the development enriched the lives of its residents and the community of Cupertino as a whole. In other words, we felt the most effective approach would be to ground our story in humanity. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:15:31', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', '61bfceb9-5161-4e42-8c23-bc2476691b49'),
 ('44', '319', 'en_us', '<h1>See the Unseen</h1>\n<p>To make a video for a development that didnt exist yet, we partnered with the amazing creatives at Steelblue LLC to create 3D animated renderings of the complex with real and computer generated people in each space.</p>\n<p>First, they built out the CGI spaces with camera moves so we could make them consistent with the live-action shots. To make these homes feel active and alive, we asked Steelblue to fill up a green screen studio with a ton of extras. In fact, it was the most extras Steelblue had ever included in a single scene. It was also the first time they shot live extras swimming in a CGI pool. Using this combination of animation, interviews, aerial imagery, and B-roll footage, Bokeh made a real estate video with life and heart.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:15:31', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', '16255779-70ef-40df-a356-63f3282af01e'),
 ('45', '320', 'en_us', '<h1>The Cut-downs</h1>\n<p>Its not easy to cover every detail of a multi-million dollar development in a single video. So we created a short series of topical cutdowns that highlighted The Hamptons most impressive features.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:15:31', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', 'f6044fda-135f-40cf-adbf-cfe2f4a61989'),
 ('46', '321', 'en_us', '<h1>Hallelujah Housing</h1>\n<p>The Hamptons passed the city council and the master plan was approved. Hallelujah! We have housing.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:15:31', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', '16197a23-4eae-407f-8205-8e582c4971fc'),
 ('47', '323', 'en_us', '<h1>Nobodys inspired by jargon</h1>\n<p>Our creative approach was predicated on the belief that human connection is not driven by jargon or statistics. For a creative brand like Instagram, an emotional, relatable, and down-to-earth approach felt more powerful. Connection is not fostered by large, immobile production teams, so we strategized a plan that kept our footprint lean, our production value high, and placed a heavy value on agility. Then we tested this plan by developing a concept film and animatic.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:18:52', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'c6c5a754-e566-4c0f-831f-77c47b36d31f'),
 ('48', '324', 'en_us', '<h1>Non-stop</h1>\n<p>Coordinating with teams around the world put the agency on a 24-hour schedule. At one point, Bokeh was filming in three countries simultaneously.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:18:52', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', '86604540-53ad-4e31-8e1b-a3be3aa728fe'),
 ('49', '325', 'en_us', '<h1>Breaking the Rules</h1>\n<p>By keeping the creative and production light-on-its feet we kept ourselves open to be inspired by the businesses we profiled. For Dubai Tourism we invited our partner from Instagram on a whim to accidently skip an afternoon of video calls to ride ATVs into the Arabian desert. This allowed us to show Dubai as multi-faceted with both urban and natural landscapes. For Mercedes-Benz we figured a down-to-earth approach did no justice for their brand. We wanted to feel the speed and energy of their vehicles so we went out to their test track in Stuttgart, and up to the skies.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:18:52', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'e8518300-d560-46b8-b5bf-2b971ec05fb8'),
 ('50', '326', 'en_us', '<h1>The payoff</h1>\n<p>The assets that we created were leveraged across a variety of channels, from keynote presentations to social and Vimeo, paid media, and the Instagram for Business blog.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:18:52', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'ed4cb26d-c728-4077-863f-b0bcb7591f1c'),
 ('51', '327', 'en_us', '<h1>Services</h1>\n<ul><li>Workshops</li><li>Strategy</li><li>Design</li><li>Brand Book &amp; Guidelines</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:26:02', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '7f6dbf51-249c-4229-979a-d889ec9738cc'),
 ('52', '328', 'en_us', '<h1>Talk it Out</h1>\n<p>Philz need a distinct vision, mission, and set of values that could be embraced internally and expressed in every decision they made. So we conducted individual interviews, a series of leadership workshops, and a company off-site to provide safe spaces to debate ideas and tinker with concepts. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:26:02', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'c9633bdb-d7fc-47b6-b886-86ebf3d2c060'),
 ('53', '329', 'en_us', '<h1>Trippin on research</h1>\n<p>White-space exercises and market research helped us create a profile for the typical Philz customer and to understand the perception of the Philz brand compared to that of its competitors. </p>\n<p>Our research survey in San Franciscos Bay Area, Los Angeles, and Washington, D.C. complemented the statistical analysis with in-person observations and on-site customer interviews.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:26:02', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '2d671ed0-c662-4748-8546-42a82afa860f'),
 ('54', '331', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>The team at Google Play was certain about two things. First, they wanted a video to commemorate the April Fools holiday. Second, they wanted the video to involve pets. With these parameters outlined, Bokeh went to work to develop a hilarious and entertaining video to introduce <em>Google Play for Pets</em>.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:30:20', '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '05d0da44-100e-4599-befd-fa1c743ddf26'),
 ('55', '332', 'en_us', '<h1>Services</h1>\n<ul><li>Film/Video</li><li>Animation</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:30:20', '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '83711ce7-34fb-4805-a730-183d80c64fa4'),
 ('56', '333', 'en_us', '<h1>Make it believable</h1>\n<p>We made the conscious decision to avoid cheap laughs and cute gimmicks; to create an April Fools video that took itself and its intent to lead the audience astray seriously. The storyand the product at its centerhad to be grounded in a real-world logic that the viewer could almost follow. We needed to develop a product idea that was simple, and solved a real human issue.</p>\n<p>Our proposal: Google Play is introducing a new category of apps in the Play Store to help pet owners train their pets and keep them occupied while theyre away.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:30:20', '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '64204741-0944-4d19-9c9a-d40bf2c3926e'),
 ('57', '334', 'en_us', '<h1>The payoff</h1>\n<p>With over 1.6M views across YouTube and Facebook, <em>Google Play for Pets </em>was featured as one of the top April Fools pranks of 2017 by publications like <strong>Adweek</strong> and <strong>CNET</strong>.</p>\n<p><br /></p>\n<p><br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:30:20', '2017-10-25 17:44:27', '680e6114-0e64-4b32-9fcd-1e376942e8d7'),
 ('58', '335', 'en_us', NULL, 'You guys are literally amazing - thank you for dealing w/ this crazy last minute madness.\"', 'Meghan Lyons', 'Brand Marketing Manager, Google Play', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', NULL, '2017-10-03 18:30:20', '2017-10-25 17:44:27', '1f06eb4e-0d05-46bb-82cc-bd061a425114'),
 ('59', '337', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>Airbnb noticed an interesting trend in Europe: A large percentage of Easyjet travellers are also avid Airbnb users. So in March 2017, Bokeh was asked to design a print ad to push Airbnb Experiences on the bottom third of all home-printed Easyjet boarding passes en route to Barcelona.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:33:30', '2017-10-24 17:29:35', '1b6fcc53-9ec7-4f8c-8141-5b0bcd0405d0'),
 ('60', '338', 'en_us', '<h1>Make it Interactive</h1>\n<p>The downside to boarding passes is that passengers just throw them away. For print-at-home boarding passes, little to no attention is paid to the lower quadrant of the page. Understandably, Airbnb did not want an ad with their logo to be ignored and dumped in the trash. </p>\n<p>Our thought process was simple: For Easyjet passengers, the lack of seat-back entertainment means that there are limited ways to stay occupied during a flight. What might capture their attention? A game. By playing a game, the passengers entertain themselves for five minutes and Airbnb is given five minutes of their attention. We decided to pitch a crossword puzzle.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:33:30', '2017-10-24 17:29:35', '1447d8ea-3589-40bb-8ce4-4fc27977449b'),
 ('61', '339', 'en_us', '<h1>Keep it simple</h1>\n<p>We identified a list of words that related to Barcelona and some of the Experiences a traveller may partake in through Airbnb. We figured out how these words could fit together and came up with clues that were clever enough to keep the game fun, but easy enough to solve. (Safe to say, we went through many iterations.)</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:33:30', '2017-10-24 17:29:35', 'd571e54d-43bb-488a-845a-5091646c066a'),
 ('62', '340', 'en_us', '<h1>The payoff</h1>\n<p>The final ad ran on over 200,000 boarding passes for all Easyjet flights to Barcelona from continental Europe during March 2017. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:33:30', '2017-10-24 17:29:35', '082e0943-717a-4adb-a82e-9812c5adefce'),
 ('63', '342', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>To announce the launch of Google Streetview and the Google Maps mobile application in Turkey, Bokeh was asked to produce an inspiring anthem video. However, there was one hurdle: No map data or Streetview imagery would be accessible. To be successful, our stylistic approach had to be less reliant on the availability of digital imagery and more attached to the target markets culture.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:37:28', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', 'caf85656-1f8b-40ef-ab61-6e052d3dcbfb'),
 ('64', '343', 'en_us', '<h1>Streetview minus the street view</h1>\n<p>How do you showcase a new feature without actually showing the feature? Establishing a partnership with DJI gave us the resources to shoot incredible aerial photography wherever we went. By combining this footage with hyperlapse photography and motion animation, we could mimic Satellite View in Google Maps and the user experience of moving between panoramas in Streetview.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:37:28', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', 'b32f8da7-82e4-484e-a322-7c1be550961b'),
 ('65', '344', 'en_us', '<h1>From the Watchtower</h1>\n<p>We reached out to Leonardo Dalessandri, the Italian director of the short film Watchtower of Turkey. Watchtower captured the essence of Turkish culture; a balanced, artistic survey of Turkeys people, customs, food, and landscapes. The video had amassed millions of views within Turkey, and from a marketing perspective incorporating Leos aesthetic would establish an immediate point-of-reference for users. The awe-inspiring, kinetically entrancing nature of the approach combined with Googles reach could give the video virality.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:37:28', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', 'c1f76f40-3ae9-48f5-8449-85ded5640e64'),
 ('66', '345', 'en_us', NULL, '\"This is super slick. Well done all around. Never seen anything quite like this The transitions between the various elements are so seamless.\"', 'Gopal Shah', 'Product Manager, Google Earth', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', NULL, '2017-10-03 18:37:28', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', '5c15822d-9946-4ab2-b5a7-18e725cab510'),
 ('67', '346', 'en_us', '<h1>Hello Turkey</h1>\n<p>Over the course of three weeks, we trekked across Istanbul and visited locales Izmir, Ephesus, eme, and irince.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:37:28', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', 'cb718c54-9db5-4d3c-9233-70327ece2a3d'),
 ('68', '347', 'en_us', '<h1>The Payoff</h1>\n<p>Perhaps the most incredibly cinematic and dynamic Google Maps launch video ever made suffered the most anticlimactic of fates. Never formally released due to the political climate in Turkey.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:37:28', '2017-10-24 17:25:55', '627c8553-2468-48b4-af52-529cfdcdb4ac'),
 ('70', '352', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>To create and evolve a series of colorful, entertaining animated videos that could visualize Googles reCAPTCHA, a technical online security product for verifying a users identity thats engineered to be less noticeable.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:41:11', '2017-10-20 21:10:43', '74479f91-8f1d-40a2-9ce0-44081b33bdf7'),
 ('71', '353', 'en_us', '<h1>Gotta CAPTCHA All</h1>\n<p>CAPTCHA is the virtual door that exists between you and the thing you really want to dolike make a safe and secure online purchase. But CAPTCHA lives completely in a digital world. We decided that an animated approach would be the easiest way to help people understand the technology. To keep things intelligible, but relatable, we borrowed the 8-bit Space Invader characters used on the reCAPTCHA website to represent malicious malware. We never gave them backthe Invaders became a major motif in the following videos. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:41:11', '2017-10-20 21:10:43', '142d5305-02d4-43ff-96e5-c47a459581cc'),
 ('72', '354', 'en_us', '<h1>Nothing to See Here No, Really.</h1>\n<p>For the second video, we were asked to visualize the concept of invisibility. We brainstormed a little Rube Goldbergesque machine to represent the complicated processes happening behind the scenes. Our motion designer, Tom, began exploring cute new ways to depict our pesky Invaders with antics like sneaking through an airport security line with a sweet stache. A few cats started showing up as well, but that wasnt exactly planned.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:41:11', '2017-10-20 21:10:43', '99680444-056f-4c1d-bc11-fcf08acee0f9'),
 ('73', '355', 'en_us', '<h1>One More Time, with Feeling.</h1>\n<p>Google asked us for a third video, but the only new thing was that reCAPTCHA was available on Android API. We took this as a creative challenge and pushed the animation by introducing new Invader shenanigans.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:41:11', '2017-10-20 21:10:43', 'f0c14b71-3d2b-42c8-90f8-5bc865f74d3b'),
 ('74', '356', 'en_us', '<h1>The Payoff</h1>\n<p>The videos received nearly 2.5 million views on YouTube. But our biggest gain was the creative latitude to develop and refine our animation skills.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 18:41:11', '2017-10-20 21:10:43', '0fa4b678-154a-4b71-a0ea-7e73dfd0fd9c'),
 ('75', '361', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>Since launching Trips in November 2016, Airbnb Experiences has connected travellers with classes, tours, and activities hosted by locals in a handful of cities around the world with one blaring exception: <strong>New York City</strong>. A little under two weeks before launch, Airbnb asked Bokeh to conceptualize and execute a true multichannel production. We captured five unique experiences in each of the five boroughs in just four days of production to create assets leveraged across marketing, PR, social, and in-product.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:15:36', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', '6e213321-acf5-4a35-b331-3305d546ceb7'),
 ('76', '362', 'en_us', '<h1>Services</h1>\n<ul><li>Film/Video</li><li>Photography</li><li>Social</li><li>Product</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:15:36', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', '53eb1ea9-3422-4bae-9981-76c1d9bc1c99'),
 ('77', '363', 'en_us', '<h1>All Together Now</h1>\n<p>On the front end, we wrangled together Airbnbs product marketing, PR, social and art departments in the same room to help identify individual objectives, and shape the larger picture for our production. After reviewing each teams wish list of content, we consolidated them to create an production approach that would fulfill everyones needs.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The production was shaped around our anthem video for product marketing. Leveraging this infrastructure, we choreographed a Camera B team to collect in-product trailers for the Airbnb app, the photographer to collect PR content, and am iPhonographer to capture vertical assets for Instagram and Instagram stories.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:15:36', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', '2eb28b73-1735-4c7d-92fe-408b591b6356'),
 ('78', '364', 'en_us', '<h1>Empire State of Mind</h1>\n<p>We wanted to embody the attitude and swagger of New York City. For the video that meant paying homage to New Yorks jazz and hip hop culture with the soundtrack, as well as employing a quick-cut editing style and dynamic movements. These gritty exterior shots were layered with displays of genuine human connection and discovery on the part of our guestsregular people (not models) who joined us on each Experience.</p>\n<p> </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:15:36', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', '7f48e7c6-8582-42e4-9e73-32913b7b2f14'),
 ('79', '365', 'en_us', '<h1>The Payoff</h1>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:15:36', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', '198d2038-6bcc-49a1-8265-bb319ae482b6'),
 ('80', '368', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>To make Airbnb a more functional app for travelers during a trip, Airbnb partnered with Resy to offer a curated list of restaurantsfrom local favorites to award winnersand make it easy to book a table right in the app. Bokeh was asked to develop an illustration style to create a fun animated video and email campaign to announce the launch of this new feature in 16 major markets across the U.S.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:21:49', '2017-10-23 18:26:55', '2f5ea9d7-b826-49ea-804a-a4c14ab3dc28'),
 ('81', '369', 'en_us', '<h1>Swede and simple</h1>\n<p>We wanted to explore integrating the photorealistic UI of the product into the illustrated animation. This combination allowed us to actually show Resy in action on the Airbnb app, creating a video that was informative and clear, but also colorful and entertaining.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-03 23:21:49', '2017-10-23 18:26:55', '7d4458a9-9821-4836-86af-18e35b5446ae'),
