 ('148', '825', 'en_us', NULL, 'Ive worked with Bokeh on a number of projects. They consistently deliver beautiful content while remaining extremely agile in dealing with the evolving landscape of technology - something rare to find in an agency.', 'Dave Kim', 'Producer Marketing Manager, Uber', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', NULL, '2017-10-12 22:59:13', '2017-10-25 18:21:09', '327ba054-85de-4f7a-9109-dd35b803f037'),
 ('149', '845', 'en_us', '<p>For the animated portions, we based our color palette around green and yellow, the colors used in the app rather than Airbnbs signature Rausch. By utilizing Kazan and Beach, we offered a fresh take on Airbnbs palette while still keeping it tied to the brand.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-18 23:20:53', '2017-10-23 18:26:55', 'db9334c5-c6ac-41e1-a4ed-9a5b65373da5'),
 ('150', '846', 'en_us', '<p>It was also important to use an illustration style that was light and simple, with lots of lines rather than dense shapes that could conflict with the app. This directive led us to Swedish illustrator Jonas Mosesson. The resulting illustrations he did trended on Dribbles home page for several days.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-18 23:20:53', '2017-10-23 18:26:55', '7cf7c26e-0315-46ea-9c98-31e23bc89fd9'),
