 ('161', '869', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-19 23:17:34', '2017-10-24 23:43:07', '640be70d-b317-485b-baab-15411116bb04'),
 ('163', '871', 'en_us', '<p>The end goal was to show that the hosts were products of New York and the experiences were products of the hosts; these adventures could not happen anywhere else. This intent permeated through all of our work: photography included portraits of each host in their respective locations surrounded by the elements of their experiences, from bespoke hats to Greek tapas, and social media assets were shaped as takeovers so the hosts could communicate to Airbnbs audiences in a way that was both casual and captivating.</p>\n<p>The deliverables were colorful, real and packed with sincere exploration and camaraderie.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 00:17:05', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', 'f296b95c-d179-4e2c-95a5-d11901497f92'),
 ('164', '905', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/239024086', 'Yonder & Airbnb | Building Memorable Experiences Together', NULL, NULL, NULL, '235-1', '2017-10-20 17:01:21', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', 'ff18f6ad-d80c-4b4b-bd3d-629bfea019f3'),
 ('167', '930', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 18:19:37', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', '1a47b366-25e2-429b-ac2a-eae2e4a0ef9e'),
 ('168', '931', 'en_us', '<p>We found Steve Frellick of Yonder Luxury Home Rentals in Asheville, North Carolina. Steve was on the brink of foreclosure during the recession of 2008 when his bank asked him to convert the family home he built into a vacation rental. Today, Yonder manages over 80 properties throughout North and South Carolina.</p>\n<p>Steves story not only encapsulates an inherently American narrative, but his humility, passion, and empathy for his guests aligned his approach with Airbnbs ethos of seeking common interests and forging connections. As a native of North Carolina, we felt Steves story would resonate with an audience in Orlando, many of whom were from the Southeast and lived through the Great Recession themselves.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 18:21:15', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', '6adde6a8-3a5a-49fa-95b6-9573645a3191'),
 ('169', '933', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 18:33:27', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', '2c704e04-d945-45a6-9dd3-b9b9b923b1e1'),
 ('172', '936', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 18:48:07', '2017-10-25 17:26:27', 'a88c98ce-29f2-46ac-b68f-da5cb829b69a'),
 ('175', '949', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 21:10:21', '2017-10-20 21:10:43', 'e344ca92-42f2-47ae-99d9-095c3ef00a1f'),
 ('177', '953', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 21:53:52', '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '19cd330e-d04a-4b4e-b7ca-e4c94ac25052'),
 ('179', '956', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-20 22:29:05', '2017-10-25 17:44:27', '4906ef79-d10d-4b22-b3e5-801ffe6bfd5d'),
 ('180', '958', 'en_us', '<h1>Mission</h1>\n<p>Financial management company Wealthfront offers software and apps to help people oversee their money in a straightforward way using robotic algorithms. Bokeh was brought on to make an informational animated video for the launch of Wealthfronts new product, Path, a visual app that makes it easy for people to plan, track, and save for retirement. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:23:40', '2017-10-25 17:54:20', '98017616-07ce-4eb7-aff7-917c628aae29'),
 ('182', '960', 'en_us', '<h1>Wheel it out</h1>\n<p>Wealthfront already had an illustration style and color palette in place on its site and wanted the video to fit that framework. Additionally, they asked us to convey a sense of active lifestyle. With these parameters, as well as the ultimate goal to make the product information engaging, we opted for a narrative centered around a female bicyclista metaphor for the ups and downs in life. We finessed the design to make sure it felt native to the existing site and used visual cues, such as increasingly expensive cars and larger homes, to illustrate the technical talking points in a lighthearted manner.  </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:23:40', '2017-10-25 17:54:20', '9ef2544c-af6e-44c6-ad12-1ebe5383c75e'),
 ('183', '961', 'en_us', '<h1>The payoff</h1>\n<p>This video was used in e-mail blast to Wealthfronts vast audience of users to inform them about Path. This animation was also used on the main landing page for the dedicated Path website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:23:40', '2017-10-25 17:54:20', '288c8d5d-c3f1-4330-b11c-21be60ef1340'),
 ('184', '963', 'en_us', NULL, '\"Bokeh hit it out of the park again, with a delightful product film that was at once educational, fun to watch, and creatively distinct.\"', 'Farzad Sharif', 'Product Marketing Manager, Trips', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', NULL, '2017-10-23 18:24:44', '2017-10-23 18:26:55', '286d7121-0bdb-43ba-a463-d2091ae04cc3'),
 ('185', '964', 'en_us', '<h1>Mission</h1>\n<p>The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reached out to Bokeh to create a high-level anthem video for World Environment Day, June 5, 2015. The videos message was that if everyone did their part (reduce electricity usage, be mindful of water usage, recycle, etc.), then it would have a big impact on the environment. The hitch? We had one month to make it happen and no time to travel around the world to get specific shots. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:28:43', '2017-10-25 17:48:17', 'bfef0c86-ac4d-43bc-b423-348892fc1f4d'),
 ('187', '966', 'en_us', '<h1>Stock up</h1>\n<p>Using stock footage to create an authentic, meaningful video is always a challenge. But to add a layer of complexity, the director we worked with, Leonardo Dalessandri, has a distinct, fluid editing style with seamless transitions and dramatic pacing. We challenged ourselves to find stock footage that matched all of our requirements, spending two weeks scouring stock sites and pulling what we thought might fit, sending it to Leonardo, and working from there. Repeating this process, we finally found enough content to build our story and create a film that is empathic and genuine.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:28:43', '2017-10-25 17:48:17', 'a64506e5-0b2d-4fe3-9aa8-f15a603234bc'),
 ('188', '967', 'en_us', '<h1>The payoff</h1>\n<p>UNEP pushed the video out on all their respective channels (Facebook, website, and news articles) and even played it on the massive LG display at New Yorks Times Square. UNEP also showed the video at many of UNEPs displays throughout the 2015 Expo in Milan, Italy.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:28:43', '2017-10-25 17:48:17', '1d50b64e-04af-4c57-a75c-c3dafbdce343'),
 ('189', '968', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>ON24, a webinar marketing platform that offers branded video and presentation software to businesses, wanted a B2B product video that was informational, but unconventional. We challenged ourselves to level up with a hybrid live-action and integrated motion graphic approach to make a traditional B2B commercial fresh and fun.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:37:56', '2017-10-23 18:39:06', 'e7f85f51-789c-4cf6-9333-edcb181aff88'),
 ('190', '969', 'en_us', '<h1>Gettin\' Disney with it</h1>\n<p>To properly demonstrate the webinar software, the video needed to be set in an office. But, rather than use a typical, boring office environment, we created an abstract workplace in an all-white cyclorama studio. This set-up also lent itself well to the overall metaphor that even though the client and marketer are sitting next to each other, they cant connectuntil ON24 saves the day of course.</p><p>We layered these live-action office scene with motion graphics. The trick was to make the graphics feel as integrated with the live shots as possible to make the product shine and keep viewers engaged. This included having an animated Twitter bird tug at the characters hair, floating icons, and a screen pop-up and rustle a pile of papers on a desk.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 18:37:56', '2017-10-23 18:39:06', '311358dd-c5e8-44fb-830a-7f2ba4f2f04b'),
 ('191', '971', 'en_us', '<h1>Payoff</h1>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 20:07:25', '2017-10-25 18:21:09', 'cb720515-bd7a-4fa8-bd0b-b47d03d8bc60'),
 ('192', '974', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 20:41:20', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '4b5700b1-a4e0-4572-8407-08eacb89403a'),
 ('194', '979', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 20:55:29', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '98acf311-91fd-489d-a832-239bc3e1bffa'),
 ('195', '981', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Philz\' color palette are distinct and ownable; fresh yet familiar. \"It\'z the best brown\" contains notes of burgundy and purple infusing the color with a sense of love and passion. \"Mint mojito\" is charismatic, light-hearted and refreshing. \"Original mug\" is bold and friendly, and pays homage to the iconic mug that stood front-and-center the original logo.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 20:59:47', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '7278ff5e-3873-4431-8972-4787522f558c'),
 ('196', '983', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Survey-takers were asked to imagine Philz, Starbucks, Peet\'s and Blue Bottle as a person. In their responses, we identified the quintessential traits that make Philz customers unique.', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 21:25:25', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '519e4a81-c43f-4760-98dd-d4783bac12fe'),
 ('197', '985', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The \"z\" speaks to Philz\' heritage. It is strong and recognizable. The foxtail hooks at the ends of the letterforms are reminiscent of the original logo. Underneath the arch of the word mark we pay homage to the promise Philz makes to each customer. Finally, the word mark is garnished with a sprig of mint and a dash of love - a of Philz\' light-hearted and warm personality.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 21:37:56', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '2d9cf358-1a9f-4e27-a95a-f01d1ef555d0'),
 ('198', '987', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 21:43:07', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '243d3868-f420-4b0f-8d1f-7bad514f677e'),
 ('199', '1001', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 23:05:11', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'ba022a3b-4221-4bfd-88ec-6c0f714ea34a'),
 ('200', '1002', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 23:05:11', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '5bfa5e2a-d976-4dbb-86cc-1a886acdae75'),
 ('201', '1007', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 23:05:11', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'b59e2ca1-88ea-4611-b12a-f61199eecc55'),
 ('202', '1008', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 23:05:11', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '8d0d6cbb-d886-4062-ad7c-0147ee1c45fc'),
 ('203', '1016', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The new word mark logo speaks to Philz humanity and realness. It is handwritten with slight imperfections in the letterforms that feel natural in execution and undaunted in confidence.', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-23 23:27:20', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', 'f3ccecdb-bb8d-48d7-8272-0cf34a1cdf09'),
 ('204', '1019', 'en_us', '<h1>A Birds Eye View</h1>\n<p>We decided to include a lot of overhead shots in the production. To make it happen, we purchased a small camera jib andwith more than a little anxietywe attached our $50K camera rig on top. Once the setup was secure, we were able to capture unique shots and enjoy the expanded possibilities of art direction and framing. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 17:17:03', '2017-10-25 18:21:09', '7a3ad5f1-2b1b-4025-abaa-881c21591655'),
 ('206', '1024', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CEO Jacob Jaber explores the feeling of screen printing a new Philz word mark.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 20:04:30', '2017-10-24 20:23:03', '21e52e7a-8450-4d75-99ae-1ea8968a53ad'),
 ('207', '1027', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 22:33:08', '2017-10-24 22:35:29', 'dfe7381f-60c3-4823-b0a8-b5e2b988ae2c'),
 ('208', '1029', 'en_us', '<h1>The Mission</h1>\n<p>Citizen is an online tool that helps students fill out the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA), turning the complicated task of filling out government forms into a streamlined process with easy-to-understand questions. The start-up needed a video that could serve as an overview and a tutorial. It would require some creative visuals to make this dry information compelling. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 22:48:10', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', '0bc4a756-c053-461e-a954-7273ec321b6a'),
 ('209', '1030', 'en_us', '<h1>Service</h1>\n<ul><li>Animation</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 22:48:10', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', 'c4d6a9af-2640-4691-9cc4-98cf831ea62e'),
 ('210', '1031', 'en_us', '<h1>Heres Looking at You, Kid</h1>\n<p>To introduce Citizen, we crafted a story around a teenage girl and her mother applying for FAFSA. The teenager served as our narrator. Balancing an appropriate amount of story alongside UI demonstrations allowed us to showcase Citizens product while aligning the perspective of the video with that of Citizens target demographic.</p>\n<p>Of course, its not a Bokeh animation unless we throw in a few Easter eggs (namely, cats). From placing felines in different scenes to a  Go Wildcats banner in the school, our motion designer may have gone a bit kitty-crazy.</p><p> </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 22:48:10', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', '7faeb232-833b-424e-a489-3baa5b605508'),
 ('211', '1033', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 22:49:59', '2017-10-25 18:21:09', '46c476ff-0987-4a56-84f3-54de19c8b068'),
 ('212', '1035', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/154131379', 'Citizen FAFSA', NULL, NULL, NULL, '16-9', '2017-10-24 23:26:04', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', 'db75ee9e-a5df-4341-abd6-c363721c00d6'),
 ('213', '1043', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 23:35:27', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', '4e401c75-6f2b-4271-8979-a57fc4561895'),
 ('214', '1051', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 23:37:20', '2017-10-25 19:09:36', 'a3038bea-b42f-401d-97e8-340d9eb13626'),
 ('215', '1054', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2017-10-24 23:46:30', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'bb245efa-f2a0-4e77-876f-61bf4cc175e7'),
 ('216', '1056', 'en_us', '<h1>Mocking the microsite</h1>\n<p>As part of the conceptualization process, we were tasked with envisioning the user experience on desktop and mobile devices in order to recommend approaches for the UX/UI design of the Local Guides microsite. This meant that our photography needed to work across platforms in both vertical and horizontal orientations. To ensure our images did that, we built out wireframe mockups of the website.</p>\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-25 17:36:01', '2017-10-25 17:36:01', '2dab3517-1122-4e5f-b063-ec95e3d1bb4b'),
 ('217', '1057', 'en_us', '<h1>Cmon get appy</h1><p>To start, we needed to bring the joke home by dreaming up with an assortment of Play for Pets apps that were believable enough for people to look up. After creating all of the animal puns we could muster, we designed a new series of fun app icons to match. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '6de7bbe4-c8ed-4074-b011-3f4dec9fe6f4'),
 ('218', '1058', 'en_us', '<h1>Cat-ing Call</h1><p>In perhaps our most unusual casting call yet, we asked Google employees (Googlers) to lend their pets and personalities to the production. While we had plenty of Dooglers apply, we made a special effort to include actors of all kinds, including Altair the turtle, Pom Pom the chinchilla, and Noodle the chicken (an absolute primadonna).</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-25 17:44:26', '2017-10-25 17:44:26', 'b318f8c8-dc1b-41ef-9009-6f346b43fcb5'),
 ('219', '1059', 'en_us', '<h1>Compose Yourself</h1>\n<p>To amp up the videos emotional impact, we needed a score that would touch hearts. We fell in love with the music (and name) of Icelandic composer Jhann Jhannsson, who had recently been nominated for an Oscar nomination for <em>The Theory of Everything</em>. We reached out to him and persuaded him to donate his talents to saving the world (he agreed). </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-25 17:47:46', '2017-10-25 17:48:17', '2babb5cc-e354-4864-b469-6e9eeba78047'),
 ('220', '1061', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-10-26 00:32:24', '2017-10-26 00:32:24', 'f1473633-78db-4405-bc90-d05d905bf48c');
