 ('4', 'field', '10', 'en_us', ' the mission on november 17 2016 airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history just five weeks earlier bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line working alongside engineering brand product marketing art and c level teams we developed myriad content to educate users on new features advertise and build awareness on social media and ultimately to introduce the world to airbnb trips on stage at airbnb open in los angeles services conceptbranding animationfilm videoanimationdigital adssocial ads 1024x1024 let s get functional humanity is a core component of the airbnb brand every feature and service built into the new airbnb app derives value from the way it connects to guests hosts and experiences to reinforce this connection we melded organic live action footage with engaging ui animations and garnished it all with a touch of whimsy the result was twelve functional product videos viewable in landscape and portrait mode introducing experiences https vimeo com 193177317 introducing itinerary https vimeo com 193177901 introducing co hosting https vimeo com 193177150 introducing social impact experiences https vimeo com 193177011 staying connected in cuba https vimeo com 193176889 y fwa sjd ceo of airbnb brian chesky this film brought the house down i cannot imagine now having done this without it show the reveal with two days before airbnb open brian needed a hail mary he lacked a centerpiece for the launch announcement that firmly connected airbnb s digital product with the human experiences it fosters so he asked us to apply our creative approach to the keynote anthem and make a film about the future of home sharing welcome to the world of trips aired during airbnb open 2016 keynote 16 9 https vimeo com 193175968 airbnb collections teaser aired during ao 2016 keynote 235 1 https vimeo com 193184792 marketing master blaster to build awareness we applied this approach to four 15 second advertisements blasted across digital and social channels burlesque https vimeo com 194444259 samurai https vimeo com 193185940 runner https vimeo com 193185835 scenester https vimeo com 193186104 the bow on top every piece of content featured a reimagined airbnb motion logo consistent with the fluid design aesthetic we developed for our animations trip airbnb logo the payoff the assets were leveraged across a variety of channels from airbnb open to product landing pages social and youtube email newsletters and paid media the functional videos amassed over 11 million views in less than three weeks on airbnb product pages the video click through rate reached as high as 15 percent we received coverage in the nytimes adweek travel leisure techcrunch mashable the telegraph and fast company '),
