 ('682', 'field', '10', 'en_us', ' the mission uberrush uses uber s network of drivers and bicycle couriers to pick up and deliver items from stores and retailers that don t offer delivery launching in new york we used the city as our backdrop and focused on three delivery categories food indie fresh a mason jar meal company clothing sam lex an upscale boutique and flowers ode a la rose a flower shop services film video uberrush your on demand network 16 9 https vimeo com 138801682 uber rush 10 uber rush 4 uber rush 12 uber rush 5 uber rush 6 producer marketing manager uber dave kim i ve worked with bokeh on a number of projects they consistently deliver beautiful content while remaining extremely agile in dealing with the evolving landscape of technology something rare to find in an agency show made in manhattan with the location new york and the shops indie fresh sam lex and ode a la rose locked in our creative attention went toward infusing our video with the vim and vigor of manhattan our narrative followed goods en route from store to customer while employing a quick cut editing style that built momentum the one rub the uberrush app was not ready by the start of physical production so we anticipated user interactions and then used a green screen app to track the finger movements of our actors when the product was built we were able to easily attach it to the screen so that the ui was visually crisp and perfectly aligned uber rush 7 a bird s eye view we decided to include a lot of overhead shots in the production to make it happen we purchased a small camera jib and with more than a little anxiety we attached our $50k camera rig on top once the setup was secure we were able to capture unique shots and enjoy the expanded possibilities of art direction and framing uber rush 11 uber rush 13 uber rush 1 uber top uber top2 uber top 3 payoff web context '),
