 ('958', 'field', '12', 'en_us', ' mission financial management company wealthfront offers software and apps to help people oversee their money in a straightforward way using robotic algorithms bokeh was brought on to make an informational animated video for the launch of wealthfront s new product path a visual app that makes it easy for people to plan track and save for retirement '),
