 ('960', 'field', '12', 'en_us', ' wheel it out wealthfront already had an illustration style and color palette in place on its site and wanted the video to fit that framework additionally they asked us to convey a sense of active lifestyle with these parameters as well as the ultimate goal to make the product information engaging we opted for a narrative centered around a female bicyclist a metaphor for the ups and downs in life we finessed the design to make sure it felt native to the existing site and used visual cues such as increasingly expensive cars and larger homes to illustrate the technical talking points in a lighthearted manner '),
